\id JHN - KAPIN, Itama draft, Yandabing, Roy 
\h Yoan 
\toc3 Yn 
\toc2 Yoan 
\toc1 Xoulek Nimza wei Yoan byex o 
\mt2 Xoulek Nimza wei 
\mt1 Yoan 
\mt2 byex o 
\imt1 Qayeeng wei la tax o 
\ip Yoan byex Xoulek Nimza ne eno neil embei, ''Yesu e Anutu xe Qayeeng wei wo xomaxoneing me lam dei eivek xe senghoing o.'' Yoan wou nalei bei xomaxoneing bongis Yesu, Anutu Neu, me xel boulek bei, Yesu e tambiy tiwei Anutu neil zonghek bei bong e nam a qou xey a noumenam o. Yoan wou lek bei, xel wei wongis Yesu eno tyek na qou mapieing wei na mi mendei takwei takwei yo, om byex e xe qapiya ne (wei 20.31). 
\ip Myaxeeng eno Yoan neil wou xey bei, "Yesu e Qayeeng tiwei takwei eno mi dei is Anutu." Dekakom Yoan tul pavulek en lulvako wei Yesu mi wong o, en xey a bou lek bei Yesu e tambiy tiwei Anutu neil zonghek bei bong e nam me na qou xey a noumenam, me e Anutu Neu. Yoan neil wou xey is ambei nyon en lulvako qes wei Yesu wong o, de xey a xei ingwei xel valu wongis Yesu me betiwou e yo. Ekom xel valu eno embei se bongis. 
\ip Eivek sapta 13-17 Yoan tul pavulek en lul wei qandi eivek boukeing tiyon o, xel vevek embei zeim axound Yesu. Yesu toundei is e xe xel betiyeing me wong qayeeng nimza ngenong wou xel. Dekakom xel vevek qou Yesu me wo qayeeng en e, me tuw e lek xax pepeeng. Loxyus eno qayeeng yeip bei Yesu qandi lek me e xe xel betiyeing yei e. 
\ip Lul ti eno xey a mi xei lumama eivek qapiya wei Yoan o, inye kwa wei xey a qou mapieing wei xomaxoneing me na wong e wong ambei qayeeng pakeing wei lulul wei mapieing wei xel wongeingis o. Om xey a xei qayeeng wei laweeng me memiing me belet me xeiyaing me xax wain me gyovaxa wei sipsip o. 
\c 1  
\s1 Qayeeng wo xomaxoneing 
\p  
\v 1 Eivek myaxeeng selis eno Qayeeng mindei, me Qayeeng mindei is Anutu, de Qayeeng on Anutu.  
\v 2 Inye mindei is Anutu eivek myaxeeng selis. 
\p  
\v 3 Eivek Qayeeng tine eno Anutu toung lulul sapa ne dalus, de embei ma veil eno lulti se woxow nambei e toung o.  
\v 4 Mapieing toundei eivek e, me mapieing tiyon eno inyon xeiyaing wei xel xomaxoneing o.  
\v 5 De xeiyaing tiyon mi siing eivek mapetok, ekom mapetok se teyei bei sevun xeiyaing. 
\p  
\v 6 Inyei tambiy ti Anutu wong e lam, moxo lei Yoan.  
\v 7 Moxo lam ambei tambiy wei neil Xeiyaing teyei, en kandek eivek moxo eno moux alis vex dalus a ngo e xe qayeeng me bongis.  
\v 8 Moxo venaxow se xeiyaing. Qe moxo lam bei na neil xeiyaing teyei.  
\v 9 Xeiyaing on zonghek wei mi wo xeiyaing wou xomaxoneing sapa, wei lam lek tembuing o. 
\p  
\v 10 Moxo mindei lek tembuing, me eivek e eno Anutu toung tembuing, ekom xomaxoneing wei tembuing eno se yeimend wou e.  
\v 11 Moxo la beeng qes, ekom xel wei e yo eno se qou e.  
\v 12 Qe moux alis vex dalus wei qou e eno xel wongis e lei, de moxo lewexe lek xel bei xel bong ambei Anutu neu.  
\v 13 Yakyak on se umbek en mamata gyand, o lalei vineing wei xomaxoneing neing o, o lalei vineing wei mayeiw o. Qe eivek Anutu eno wo xel umbek nambei e neuyeiw. 
\p  
\v 14 De Qayeeng wo xomaxoneing me lam dei eivek xa senghoing. Xa xei e xe xeiyaing ngandoung, inyei xeiyaing ngandoung wei Neu Moux tixemou tateis wei Ma wong e lam o, pup en lalei xeiles me zonghek. 
\p  
\v 15 Yoan neilteyei wou moux alis vex en e me taxe bei, “Inyei tambiy tiwei a neil wou xam bei, ‘Tambiy tiwei lam yus en ay eno ngandoung ghanaw ay, en nambei mindei takwei en ay.’”  
\v 16 De e xe lalei xeiles wei pup eivek e yo eno xey xouing a mi qou mata lumama titi teyeima.  
\v 17 En petieing eno wong wou xey eivek Mose mema, de lalei xeiles me zonghek eno lam wou xey eivek Yesu Kilisi.  
\v 18 Xelti se mi yei Anutu, qe Neu tixemou tateis, e maxow Anutu wei mindei wou Ma wes, eno talex Anutu wou xey. 
\s1 Yoan lipekeing neilteyei bei e se Kilisi 
\p  
\v 19 De inye Yoan xe pavulek ne, gyeik xel Yudayeiw wei Yerusalem eno wong xel lumuki me Livaiyeiw la teling e bei, “Wang eti?”  
\v 20 Moxo neil teyei de se axvun qe neil teyei bei, “A se Kilisi.” 
\p  
\v 21 Xel teling e, “Woyom wang eti? Wa Eliya?” 
\p Moxo neil, “Se ay.” 
\p “Qe wa poropet tiwei xa di axe yo?” \rq Petieing 18:15-18\rq* 
\p Moxo neil embei, “Ma.” 
\p  
\v 22 Woyom xel teling e no, “Wang eti? Wa neilteyei wou xa en xa nox a neil wou xel wei wong xa lam o. Wambei neimbei wamaxow eti?” 
\p  
\v 23 Yoan neil nambei poropet Yesaya neil o, 
\q1 “A tambiy tiwei vya taxeing ti lam eivek tembuing bandaing o, 
\q2 ‘Xam pepyawexe sakwaing embo bombek en Tambiy Ngandoung.’” \rq Yesaya 40:3\rq* 
\p  
\v 24 Xel Parisi valu wei xel wong xel lam  
\v 25 eno teling e, “Wangwei wa se Kilisi, o Eliya o poropet nei yond nambei nya wang lipek xel?” 
\p  
\v 26 Yoan neil elox bei, “A lipek xam en memiing, ekom tambiy ti toungale eivek xam senghoing eno xam seng woulek.  
\v 27 Inyon tambiy tiwei lam yus en ay yo, de a se nimza teyei bei a tul yis wei e xe vaxalambes o.” 
\p  
\v 28 Lulul tine dalus qandi lek nanghei Betani wei memiing Yorodan loxalu nei, wei Yoan mi lipek moux alis vex anghei yo. 
\s1 Yesu e Anutu xe Sipsip Lingheing 
\p  
\v 29 Bouk nge eno Yoan yei Yesu di lam wou e, om neil embei, “Wei, Anutu xe Sipsip Lingheing, tambiy tiwei semaleeng sewokeing veil xomaxoneing wei tembuing sapa yo!  
\v 30 Inye tambiy tiwei a neil gyeik ingwei a neimbei, ‘Tambiy tiwei lam yus en ay eno ngandoung ghanaw ay en nambei mindei takwei gyeik a se ghei umbek o.’  
\v 31 A maxow eno a se woulek e, ekom qes wei a lam lipek xel en memiing bei bong xel Israel gyeimend wou e.” 
\p  
\v 32 Woyom Yoan neil teyei bei, “A xei Laweeng Vambuing lep me lam anghei tyoung gheyapu nei nambei beliy me la dei lek e.  
\v 33 A maxow se woulek e, qe tambiy tiwei wong a lam a lipek moux alis vex en memiing eno neil wou ay, ‘Tambiy tiwei wang wei Laweeng Vambuing lep me lam dei lek e eno tyek zipek xel en Laweeng Vambuing.’  
\v 34 A maxow a xei me na neil wou xam bei tambiy tiyon Anutu Neu Moux.” 
\s1 Xel betiyeing wei Yoan eno betiy Yesu 
\p  
\v 35 Bouk nge eno Yoan toungale inyon no is e xe betiyeing yayuw.  
\v 36 De moxo yei Yesu di la eno neil embei, “Wei, Anutu xe sipsip lingheing!” 
\p  
\v 37 Ka betiyeing yuw on ngo ingwei e neil tiyon, eno luw la betiwou Yesu.  
\v 38 Yesu pekwi ma, me yei luw di betiy e om teling, “Muw ghe di wimexe vati?” Luw neil embei, “Labai” (qes ambei nye Putoung), “wang mindei inya?” 
\p  
\v 39 Moxo neil elox bei, “Muw lam wei.” Om luw la me yei ingwei mindei eivek o, me luw mindei bouk tiyon is e. Inyon nambei seivma qou vey soukeing. 
\p  
\v 40 Andrias wei Simon Petele li yo, inyon yuw wei ngo qayeeng wei Yoan neil me betiy Yesu eno nge.  
\v 41 Andrias la yimexe li Simon me neil wou e tax bei, “Xa xei Mesia” (qes ambei nye Kilisi).  
\v 42 De Andrias qou Simon me la wou Yesu. Yesu yei e de neil, “Wa Simon Yoan neu. Tyek xel taxe wa leim bei Sipas.” (Xey a pekwi bei Petele. Qes bei qakous.) 
\s1 Yesu taxe Pilip me Natanael 
\p  
\v 43 De bouk nge eno Yesu embei na Galili. Moxo yeiwou Pilip me neil wou e bei, “Wa betiy ay.” 
\p  
\v 44 Pilip on tambiy wei Betsaida yo, wei Andrias aluw Petele bend qes.  
\v 45 Pilip la yeiwou Natanael me neil wou e, “Xa xei tambiy tiwei Mose byex eivek petieing me xel poropet byex is ambei nyon o. Inyon Yosep neu Yesu wei Nasaret o.” 
\p  
\v 46 Natanael teling, “Nasaret ei! Inye lul nimza valu tyek nam anghei inyei?” 
\p Pilip neil embei, “Lam me wei.” 
\p  
\v 47 Ka Yesu yei Natanael di lam eno moxo luk en e bei, “Tambiy tine Israel zonghek. Eivek e eno tyonyeing ma.” 
\p  
\v 48 Natanael teling, “Wang woulek ay ambei nya?” 
\p Yesu lewexe bei, “Gyeik Pilip seng ghei taxe wang eno a xei wang toundei eivek xax basunghek xeinghembi.” 
\p  
\v 49 Woyom Natanael neilteyei bei, “Putoung, wang on Anutu Neu Moux, wa king wei Israel o.” 
\p  
\v 50 Yesu neil wou e, “Wang wongis en ingwei a neil wou wang bei a xei wang toundei eivek xax basunghek xeinghembi yo. Tyek wang gwei lul ngandoung valu ghanaw inyon.”  
\v 51 Woyom moxo tetulexe no, “A neil wou wang zonghek, tyek wang gwei tyoung gheyapu natax, me Anutu xe angelayeiw mendi zek me na gheyapu de mendi douk me noum lek Xomaxoneing Neu Moux.” 
\c 2  
\s1 Yesu pekwi memiing wo wain 
\p  
\v 1 Lek bouk tiwei yal eno iingama ti qandi nanghei beyeeng Kana eivek Galili. Yesu ta la toundei inyon woy atax,  
\v 2 me Yesu is e xe xel betiyeing is ambei nyon, xel wo dik wou xel en iingama yon.  
\v 3 Gyeik ingwei wain ma, eno Yesu ta neil wou e, “Wain ma veil xel o.” 
\p  
\v 4 Yesu neil elox bei, “Tang, wang neil ambei nyon wou ay enva? Bouk wei ay eno se ghei lam.” 
\p  
\v 5 Moxo ta neil wou xel xukxe, “Xam ghe bong vati wei embei neil wou xam o.” 
\p  
\v 6 Deng qakous ngandoung limti mi nale paviy nanghei inyon, xel Yudayeiw mi lipek eivek nambei xel xe kwa. Memiing nimaying nambei 100 lita eno mi nale eivek titi. 
\p  
\v 7 Yesu neil wou xel xukxe bei, “Xam a taw memiing eivek deng qakous on xel xouing.” Om xel taw eivek me e pup. 
\p  
\v 8 Woyom moxo neil wou xel bei, “Xam zakouv valu gweimbeeng me na qou me na wou tambiy wei la tax en mata yo.” 
\p Om xel wong ambei nyon,  
\v 9 me teiv wei la tax en mata eno num me axe bei memiing pekwi wain. Moxo se woulek bei inyon lam anghei inya, qe xel xukxe wei di taw memiing eno woulek. Woyom moxo taxe moux wei embei dii vex o la beyaleing  
\v 10 me neil embei, “Xel dalus mi wong wain wei nenyeing o me xel mi num atax, deka xel num ngenong woy, xel wong ingwei lavus o me xel num yus. Ekom wang byexaxoun ingwei nimza yo de gweimbeeng kane eno wang qou me lam.” 
\p  
\v 11 Yesu wong e xe lulvako tiwei tax o nambei dee nanghei Kana, danghei wei Galili nei. Moxo talex e xe nikanzek ngandoung teyei me e xe xel betiyeing yei me wongis e. 
\p  
\v 12 Ka tine la veil eno moxo lep me la xo Kapenaom nei is ta me liyeiw me e xe xel betiyeing. Xel dei bouk valu nanghei inyei. 
\s1 Yesu tiy xel veil xomek vambuing 
\p  
\v 13 Ka bouk wo sepi lek en Yudayeiw xe Pasova, Yesu lek me la Yerusalem.  
\v 14 Eivek tete lalei wei xomek vambuing eno moxo yei xel moux di wong vateivek lek manghaxo, me sipsip me beliy, de xel valu toundei lek lelek me pakei malew wouma.  
\v 15 Om Yesu qou yis valu me viy me tiy xel vula veil xomek vambuing is sipsip me manghaxo. Moxo qapyex malew selewa wei xel di pakei eno veil de qapyex xel xe lelek is.  
\v 16 Woyom neil wou xel wei di wong vateivek lek beliy o bei, “Xam qou menek beimambei ne me la veil inye! Xam seng bong Mang xe xomek bong ambei xomek wei vateivek o!” 
\p  
\v 17 De e xe xel betiyeing wounaleind en qayeeng wei yeip eivek qapiya wei petieing o nambei nye, 
\q1 “A laleing vind wa xe xomek om a wong xuk nikanzek bei bong xomek ne na toumendei nimza.” \rq Qapiya Lalo 69:6\rq* 
\p  
\v 18 Woyom xel Yudayeiw neil wou Yesu bei, “Tyek wa talex dee wei lulvako en vati eno wou xa en xa boulek bei wang wo lei ngandoung en wambei mi bong lulti beimambei yon dalus?” 
\p  
\v 19 Yesu neil wou xel bei, “Xam lelolexe xomek vambuing tine, de tyek a dev epyap no eivek bouk yal.” 
\p  
\v 20 De Yudayeiw neil elox bei, “Xel wong xuk lek eveing xomek vambuing ne teyei lek vakovek qes mepyeiyuw me lak limti, de tyek wang dev e qandi lek eivek bouk yal?”  
\v 21 Ekom xomek vambuing wei moxo neil on inyon emaxow neing.  
\v 22 Ka Yesu qandi lek veil meyeing, e xe xel betiyeing wou naleind en vati wei e neil o. Woyom xel wongis xoulek wei di yeip eivek qapiya yo me qayeeng wei Yesu neil o. 
\p  
\v 23 Ka Yesu toundei Yerusalem eivek mata wei Pasova yo, eno xomaxoneing ngenongakes yei dee wei lulvako wei wong o me wongis e lei.  
\v 24 Ekom Yesu venaxow woulek xow om se wongis xel, en moxo woulek xomaxoneing dalus.  
\v 25 Moxo se wounalei en xelti bei na neil wou xomaxoneing, en moxo woulek vati wei toundei eivek xomaxoneing laleind o. 
\c 3  
\s1 Yesu teyoxe Nikodimas 
\p  
\v 1 De tambiy wei Parisi yo ti lei Nikodimas, inyon gyovaxa wei kanzol wei xel Yudayeiw o ti.  
\v 2 Moxo lam wou Yesu eivek boukeing me neil wou, “Putoung, xa woulek bei wang on putoung tiwei Anutu wong e lam o. Wangwei Anutu se mendei is xelti on tyek se bong dee wei lulvako yo nambei ingwei wang mi wong on.” 
\p  
\v 3 Yesu neil elox wou e bei, “A neil wou wang zonghek, xelti embei se dumbek no on tyek se gyei Anutu xe tete lalei.” 
\p  
\v 4 Nikodimas teling, “Nambei nya tambiy dumbek no gyeik ingwei wo teiv takwei yo? Neing ayang moxo tyek se nox me na eivek ta veis luyuw me dumbek no!” 
\p  
\v 5 Yesu lewexe bei, “A neil wou wang zonghek, xelti embei se dumbek en memiing me Laweeng Vambuing on tyek se na eivek Anutu xe tete lalei.  
\v 6 Lul wei neing wong e umbek eno inyon neing, de lul wei Laweeng Vambuing wong e umbek eno inyon laweeng.  
\v 7 Wa seng detek en a xe qayeeng, ‘Qe wang dumbek no.’  
\v 8 De laweeng mi vei me la danghei danghei wei embei na yo. Eno wang mi ngo nindenduing, ekom wa seng woulek bei e lam anghei inya o embei na nya. Om inyon teyei lek xel dalus wei umbek vako en Laweeng Vambuing o.” 
\p  
\v 9 Nikodimas teling, “Lulti yon tyek bong ambei nya?” 
\p  
\v 10 Yesu neil wou, “Wa Israelyeiw xe putoung, ekom wa seng woulek lulti beimambei ne?  
\v 11 A neil wou wang zonghek, xa luk en vati wei xa woulek o, me xa neil qayeeng en vati wei xa xei woy yo, ekom xam xomaxoneing seng wongis xa xe qayeeng.  
\v 12 A neil wou xam en lul wei tembuing o ekom xam seng wongis, woyom wangwei a neil wou xam en lul wei tyoung gheyapu yo on tyek xam ghe bongis ambei nya?  
\v 13 Xelti se la eivek tyoung gheyapu ti qe tambiy tiwei lam anghei tyoung gheyapu nei yo, inyon Xomaxoneing Neu Moux.  
\v 14 Inye nambei Mose zeim myeiy lek la eivek tembuing bandaing o, om Xomaxoneing Neu Moux eno tyek xel a zeim e zekna,  
\v 15 om xel dalus wei embei bongis e eno tyek na qou deing mapieing luta luta. 
\p  
\v 16 “En Anutu lalei vind xomaxoneing wei tembuing sapa yo omek wong emaxow Neu Moux tixemou tateis on, en kandek eti yeiw wei wongis e eno se mey, qe xel a qou deing mapieing luta luta.  
\v 17 En Anutu se wong Neu Moux lam lek tembuing bei e nam bong qayeeng en xomaxoneing lek tembuing. Qe wong e lam bei e nam devind xomaxoneing wei tembuing sapa veil meyeing.  
\v 18 Eti yeiw wei wongis moxo eno se nale lek qayeeng, qe eti yeiw wei se wongis e eno nale lek qayeeng woy. En nambei se wongis Anutu Neu Moux tixemou tateis on lei.  
\v 19 Xel xe qayeeng on qes ambei nye, xeiyaing lam eivek tembuing, ekom xomaxoneing laleind vind mapetok ghanaw xeiyaing en nambei xel xe kwa yon nilul.  
\v 20 Xomaxoneing sapa wei mi wo kwa nilul eno mi pesek xeiyaing, om xel embei se nam eivek xeiyaing, en tyek xel xe kwa nilul on nam yanyateiv.  
\v 21 Ekom eti yeiw wei mi betiwou kwa wei zonghek eno mi lam eivek xeiyaing en kandek xel gyei embo nimza bei lulul wei xel mi wong eno xel mi wong xuk en Anutu xe nikanzek.” 
\s1 Yoan lipekeing neil Yesu teyei no 
\p  
\v 22 Ka tine la veil, eno Yesu lis e xe xel betiyeing la danghei wei Yudia nei. Moxo toundei is xel anghei inyon me lipek moux alis vex.  
\v 23 Yoan lipek xomaxoneing is ambei nyon nanghei Ainon paviy beyeeng Salim, en nambei memiing ngenong di yeip inyon, me xomaxoneing di lam bei e zipek xel.  
\v 24 Inyon atax gyeik xel se ghei toung Yoan eivek xeitueing o.  
\v 25 Xel betiyeing wei Yoan o valu is Yuda ti pyalek ama en kwa wei xel mi lipek me wo vako wou Anutu manghalus o.  
\v 26 Yoan xe xel betiyeing lam neil wou e bei, “Putoung, tambiy tiwei toundei is wang anghei memiing Yorodan loxalu nei me wang neil e xe qayeeng, eno di lipek moux alis vex, me xel dalus la wou e.” 
\p  
\v 27 Yoan neil elox wou xel bei, “Tambiy ti teyei bei qou vatiyeiw, wangwei Anutu wei tyoung gheyapu nei bong wou e yo.  
\v 28 Xam venaxow a neil teyei en qayeeng wei a neil o bei, ‘A se Kilisi, qe a tambiy tiwei Anutu wong a lam atax en e yo.’  
\v 29 Tambiy ti dii vex ti eno vex tiyon e venei. De e xe gweleeng mi nale me li nenya wou tambiy wei ii vex o xe lukeing me wo xeilala ngandoung. Om gweimbeeng xeilala tiyon eno pup eivek a laleing.  
\v 30 Moxo lei e zekna gheyapu, de a leing e deteiwou. 
\p  
\v 31 “Tambiy tiwei lam anghei gheyapu eno la ghey en lulul sapa, de tambiy wei lam anghei tembuing eno inyon tembuing, me mi luk en lul wei tembuing o. De tambiy tiwei lam anghei tyoung gheyapu eno la ghey en lulul sapa.  
\v 32 Moxo mi luk en vati wei yei me ngo yo, ekom xelti se zeimaxoun e xe qayeeng.  
\v 33 Tambiy tiwei zeimaxoun e xe qayeeng eno talex lek bei Anutu yon zonghek ayang.  
\v 34 En tambiy tiwei Anutu wong e lam eno mi neil Anutu xe qayeeng, en Anutu wong Laweeng Vambuing dalus wou e.  
\v 35 De Ma lalei vind Neu Moux me toung lulul dalus la eivek e mema.  
\v 36 Xelti bongis Neu Moux on qou mapieing luta luta, ekom xelti pesek Neu Moux on tyek se gyei mapieing, en tyek Anutu xe lalei vanei detei lek e.” 
\c 4  
\s1 Yesu luk is vex wei Samaria yo ti 
\p  
\v 1 De Parisiyeiw ngo qayeeng bei Yesu lipek xomaxoneing me wong xel wo betiyeing ngenong ghanaw Yoan.  
\v 2 Ekom Yesu venaxow se lipek xel, qe inyon e xe xel betiyeing.  
\v 3 Yesu woulek bei xel Parisi ngo tine om la veil Yudia de lox me la Galili no. 
\p  
\v 4 Dom moxo tupwou sakwaing tiwei la senghoing eivek Samaria nei.  
\v 5 Om moxo la eivek beyeeng nayak ti lei Sikar eivek tembuing danghei wei Samaria yo. Beyeeng tiyon toundei paviy tembuing wei Yakop wong wou neu Yosep o.  
\v 6 Yakop xe leiveeng memiing ti toundei inyei, de Yesu nima en ingwei lam sakwaing anding o, om la dei paviy leiveeng memiing on. Inyon nambei seivma evlek o. 
\p  
\v 7 Gyeik Samaria vex ti lam en embei nam a puw memiing eno Yesu neil wou vexo, “Tyek wang bong memiing me a num?”  
\v 8 Moxo xe xel betiyeing la eivek beyeeng nayak en xel embei na bou lul yaeing. 
\p  
\v 9 Samaria vex neil wou e bei, “Wa Yuda ti de a Samaria vex ti. Nambei nya wang teling wou ay en numeing?” En Yudayeiw me Samariayeiw se mindei is ama. 
\p  
\v 10 Yesu lewexe wou vexo, “Wangwei wang boulek lul xeilala wei Anutu embei bong o me eti ingwei teling wang en numeing, on wa teling wou e me embong memiing wei mapieing o wou wang.” 
\p  
\v 11 Vex neil wou bei, “Teiv, deng me yis wei wambei puw memiing nangya eno ma de leiveeng memiing ne la ghembi. Tyek wa qou memiing mapieing tiyon nanghei inya?  
\v 12 Beip wang ghanaw xe bund Yakop, moxo wong leiveeng memiing tine wou xa de e venaxow is neuyeiw me manghaxo me sipsip is lul dalus mi num memiing tine?” 
\p  
\v 13 Yesu lewexe, “Xomaxoneing sapa wei mi num memiing tine eno tyek kwend a tip no,  
\v 14 ekom xelti embei num memiing wei ambei bong wou e ne tyek kwa se tip. De memiing wei ambei bong wou e eno tyek na mi puw lulaxeiv eivek e me bong mapieing luta luta wou e.” 
\p  
\v 15 De vex neil wou e bei, “Teiv, wang bong memiing tiyon wou ay en kandek a kwang se tip no de a se mi nox me noum inye en puweing memiing.” 
\p  
\v 16 Moxo neil wou vexo bei, “La, taxe leyam de muw xouing loum.” 
\p  
\v 17 Vexo neil elox bei, “A leyang ma yo.” 
\p Yesu neil wou e, “Wang neil neing, gyeik ingwei wang neimbei wa leyam ma yo.  
\v 18 En nambei wa leyam lim, de moux tiwei wang toundei is ne inye se wa leyam. Qayeeng vati wei wang neil on zonghek ayang.” 
\p  
\v 19 De vexo neil wou e bei, “Teiv, a xei bei inye wa poropet ti.  
\v 20 Xa bumiyeiw mi wong lalo lek lukendu tine, ekom xam Yudayeiw eno xam ghe mi neimbei beyeeng wei xomaxoneing a mi bong lalo eno eivek Yerusalem.” 
\p  
\v 21 Yesu neil teyei wou e bei, “Vex, wang bongis ay, bouk ti tyek nam eno tyek xam seng bong lalo wou Mang lek lukendu tine o eivek Yerusalem.  
\v 22 Xam Samariayeiw ghe mi wong lalo wou vati wei xam seng woulek o, de xa Yudayeiw a mi wong lalo wou vati wei xa woulek o, en vineing wei qou xa lam veil nilul eno lam wou xa Yuda.  
\v 23 Ekom bouk ti tyek nam, me gweimbeeng ne eno lam woy om gyeik xel embei bong lalo zonghek ond xel bong lalo wou Mang eivek Laweeng me zonghek, en Mang lalei vind xel ambei nyon bei xel a mi bong lalo wou e.  
\v 24 Anutu yon laweeng, om xel wei mi wong lalo wou e eno xel a mi bong lalo eivek Laweeng me eivek zonghek.” 
\p  
\v 25 De vexo neil embei, “A woulek bei Mesia tiwei xel mi taxe e bei Kilisi eno tyek nam. Om gyeik ingwei moxo embei nam, eno tyek na neil lul dalusateiv teyei wou xey.” 
\p  
\v 26 Woyom Yesu neilteyei wou e bei, “A tambiy tiyon, ingwei di luk is wang ne eno inye ay.” 
\s1 Xel betiyeing loumelam wou Yesu 
\p  
\v 27 Woyom ka e xe xel betiyeing loum eno xel etek en xel yei ingwei di luk is vex ti yo. Ekom xelti se teling, “Wa bei qou vati?” o “Nambei nya wang di luk is vex on?” 
\p  
\v 28 Woyom vexo ghanaw e xe memiing dengmuing toundei de lox me la beyeeng me neil wou xomaxoneing dalus nambei nye,  
\v 29 “Xam lam wei tambiy tiwei neil wou ay en lul dalus wei a mi wong takwei yo. Beip inyei Kilisi?”  
\v 30 Om xel lam veil beyeeng nayak on me la yei e. 
\p  
\v 31 Dekakom e xe xel betiyeing neil wou e bei, “Putoung, wa lulul ne.” 
\p  
\v 32 Ekom moxo neil wou xel, “A xe yaeing wei yaing eno xam seng woulek o.” 
\p  
\v 33 Woyom e xe xel betiyeing di neil wouma bei, “Beip xel valu qou lul yaeing me lam wou e?” 
\p  
\v 34 Yesu neil wou xel, “A xe lul yaeing eno nambei nye, a bei betiwou tambiy tiwei wong a lam eno lalei me na bong e xe xuk e na pyap lek.  
\v 35 Beip xam seng mi neimbei, ‘Dentouk qes vey di yeip zeyi bouk wei qekuwou lulul yaeing o?’ A neil wou xam, xam ghe gweina xuk danghei danghei nei! Lulul wo neing woy teyei lek qoueing.  
\v 36 Me gweimbeeng tambiy wei mi qekuwou lulul yaeing eno qou e xe xouveing me di qeku lul yaeing wei deing mapieing luta luta yo, om tambiy wei vuw lul o me tambiy wei wong xuk lek qoueing lulul neing o, eno luw xouing bo xeindlala.  
\v 37 Inye xel neil, ‘Tambiy nge vuw lulul eivek xuk de nge qekuwou lulul neing’ eno qayeeng ne zonghek.  
\v 38 A wong xam ghe la qekuwou lulul yaeing wei xam seng wo xuk lek o. Qe xel valu wong pok ngandoung lek, de xam ghe la qou vineing lek pok wei xel o.” 
\s1 Xel Samaria ngenong wongis 
\p  
\v 39 Xel Samaria ngenong wei beyeeng nayak tiyon eno wongis Yesu, en qayeeng wei vex on neil teyei yo, “Moxo neil wou ay en lulul dalus wei a wong takwei yo.”  
\v 40 Om gyeik ingwei Samariayeiw lam wou moxo eno xel neil wou bei e toumendei is xel, om moxo toundei bouk yayuw is xel.  
\v 41 En nambei Yesu xe qayeeng wei neil, eno moux alis vex ngenong wongis. 
\p  
\v 42 Xel neil wou vex on, “Xa se wongis en nambei vati wei wang neil o, qe gweimbeeng xa maxow a ngo me na woulek bei inye neing ayang, tambiy tine qou xey a loum veil nilul wei tembuing sapa yo.” 
\s1 Yesu wong beyeiv neu moux wo nimzalek 
\p  
\v 43 Ka bouk yuw on la veil eno Yesu la Galili.  
\v 44 Yesu venaxow neil qayeeng tine, xel se mi wevek poropet ti xeinghembi eivek emaxow beeng qes.  
\v 45 Om gyeik ingwei moxo la tyip Galili, eno Galiliyeiw wo xeindlala en e. En xel yei lul wei wong eivek Yerusalem gyeik mata wei Pasova yo, en xel la toundei inyei is. 
\p  
\v 46 Yesu lox me la beyeeng Kana eivek Galili no, wei nanghei inyon eno moxo pekwi memiing wo wain. De nanghei inyei eno king xe beyeiv ti neu moux vanei wong me e di yeip anghei Kapenaom.  
\v 47 Woyom tambiy tiyon ngo bei Yesu la veil Yudia me la toundei Galili, eno moxo la wou e me tay wou Yesu bei e nam bong e neu moux bo nimzalek, en neu e bim amey. 
\p  
\v 48 Yesu neil wou e, “Wangwei xam ne seng gwei dee wei lulvako yo ond xam seng mi wongis.” 
\p  
\v 49 King xe beyeiv neil wou e, “Teiv, wang nam axone daing enok a neung amey.” 
\p  
\v 50 Yesu neil elox wou e bei, “Wang nox en neum tyek na toumendei mapieing.” 
\p De moux tiyon wongis qayeeng wei Yesu neil o me la.  
\v 51 Ka moxo di la wou sakwaing, e xe xel xukxe lam pelong e me neil wou bei, neum toundei mapieing.  
\v 52 Woyom moxo teling xel en seivma wei neu wo nimzalek, eno xel neil wou e, “Gying ma veil e vezeiveeng soukeing wei seivma ti yo.” 
\p  
\v 53 Woyom ma woulek bei lek seivma kayon eno Yesu neil wou e, “Neum tyek na toumendei mapieing.” Om moxo is nipapu dalus wei e beeng eno wongis. 
\p  
\v 54 Inye dee wei lulvako luyuw wei Yesu wong gyeik e la veil Yudia me la toundei Galili yo. 
\c 5  
\s1 Yesu wong tambiy ti wo nimzalek nanghei lounyeing Betesda 
\p  
\v 1 Ka inyon la veil, eno Yesu lek me la Yerusalem en bouk ngandoung wei lalo wei Yudayeiw o.  
\v 2 Eivek Yerusalem paviy tete mya wei sipsip eno lounyeing ti mi yeip inyon, xel Hibru mi neil Betesda. Xomek nayak lim toukale wou lounyeing on nenyawes.  
\v 3 Xel ngenong wei vanei nelu nelu eno mi yeip eivek xomek nayak nanghei inyon, is xel wei matekeing o, me vaxa nol o me xel wei bezomb o. [ 
\v 4 En Tambiy Ngandoung xe angela ti mi lam axone eivek bouk titi me la eivek lounyeing me wo pimapi wou, de tambiy ti embei na eivek lounyeing wei di wo pimapi yon atax eno wo nimzalek veil vanei wei wong e yo.]  
\v 5 Tambiy ti vanei me e mi yeip eivek xomek nayak wei xel byex wou yon teyei lek vakovek qes 38.  
\v 6 Yesu yei moxo di yeip inyon eno woulek bei vanei wong e me e mi yeip enden, Yesu teling wou e, “Wa being bo nimzalek?” 
\p  
\v 7 Tambiy wei vanei yon neil elox bei, “Teiv, xel wei embei devind a na eivek memiing gyeik ingwei embei bo pimapi eno ma. A venaxow a mi wong me na xei en ambei na eivek, ekom xel valu mi la eivek ghanaw ay.” 
\p  
\v 8 Woyom Yesu neil wou e, “Qandi lek! De qou wa xe ghus me la.”  
\v 9 Lutika eno moux on wo nimzalek, de moxo qou e xe ghus me la. 
\p Bouk tiyon eno inye Sabat,  
\v 10 om xel teivateiv wei Yudayeiw o neil wou moux tiwei wo nimzalek o, “Inye Sabat, petieing peti bei wa se qalei wa xe ghus lek.” 
\p  
\v 11 Ekom moxo neil elox bei, “Tambiy tiwei wong a wo nimzalek eno neil wou a bei, ‘Qou wa xe ghus me la vaxam.’” 
\p  
\v 12 Om xel teling e, “Tambiy eti ingwei neil embei wa qou ghus me ghe na vaxam on?” 
\p  
\v 13 Moux tiwei wo nimzalek eno loungen tambiy tiwei neil o, en Yesu la xupekeing eivek xel ngenong senghoing me la. 
\p  
\v 14 Kalekom Yesu yei e nanghei tete lalei wei xomek vambuing nei me neil wou e, “Wei, wang wo nimzalek woy. Om wa seng nox bong sewokeing no, enok nimaying ngandoung ti qandi wou wang.”  
\v 15 Woyom moux tiyon la neil wou teivateiv wei Yudayeiw o bei, “Tambiy tiwei wong a wo nimzalek eno inyon Yesu.” 
\s1 Anutu Neu Moux wo leilaing en xuk 
\p  
\v 16 Om nambei Yesu di wong lulti beimambei yon lek Sabat, om teivateiv wei Yudayeiw di wo nol wou e.  
\v 17 Yesu neil elox wou xel, “Mang mi wo xuk taxombouk me elam gweimbeeng, me ay is ambei nyon, a mi wo xuk.”  
\v 18 En qes tine Yudayeiw mi wo niqetyei qetyei en embei nyeis Yesu na mey, en se ingwei pyalek petieing wei Sabat o, qe mi neil embei e ma Anutu. Me wong emaxow teyei lek Anutu. 
\p  
\v 19 Yesu lewexe wou xel, “A neil wou xam zonghek, Neu Moux se mi wong lulti nangya emaxow xe kwa, qe moxo tyek bong lul kawei yei Ma wong o, en nambei vatiyeiw wei Ma wong eno Neu Moux tyek bong ambei nyon.  
\v 20 En Ma lalei vind Neu Moux me talex lulul dalus wei mi wong eno wou e. De ingwei embei bong etekeing wou xam eno Ma tyek talex lul ngandoung valu wou e ghanaw inyon veil.  
\v 21 En Ma mi piyexe xel wei mey o me wong mapieing wou xel, om Neu Moux is ambei nyon, moxo mi wong mapieing wou xomaxoneing teyei lek emaxow lalei.  
\v 22 Ma se mi wong qayeeng en xelti, qe wong xuk dalus wei wongeing qayeeng eno wou Neu Moux,  
\v 23 om xel dalus a mi sanghoxe Neu Moux nambei ingwei xel mi sanghoxe Ma yo. Xelti embei se sanghoxe Neu Moux on tyek se sanghoxe Ma tiwei wong e lam o. 
\p  
\v 24 “Neing ayang, a neil wou xam, xel tiwei ngo a xe qayeeng me wongis tambiy tiwei wong a lam eno qou mapieing luta luta woy de tyek se teyei bei bale lek qayeeng me na qou myaveweeng. Qe moxo sek me lam veil meyeing woy, de la dei mapieing.  
\v 25 Neing ayang, neing ayang, a neil wou xam, bouk di lam me gweimbeeng ne eno lam gyeik ingwei xel meyeing embei ngo Anutu Neu Moux vya yo me xelti embei ngowou eno dei mapieing.  
\v 26 En Ma xe mapieing toundei eivek emaxow, om moxo wong nikanzek wou Neu Moux bei e qou mapieing eivek venaxow.  
\v 27 Me Ma wong lei ngandoung wou e bei e mi bong qayeeng en moux alis vex, en nambei e Xomaxoneing Neu Moux. 
\p  
\v 28 “Xam seng bou naleimim ngenong en qayeeng tine, en bouk di lam, gyeik ingwei xel wei mey me di yeip eivek xel xe leiveeng meyeing eno tyek na ngo e vya  
\v 29 me lam myayaing. Xel wei mi wong kwa nimza eno tyek qandi lek me mendei mapieing, de xel wei mi wong kwa nilul eno tyek qandi lek me na qou myaveweeng.  
\v 30 A maxow se mi wong lulti, qe a mi wong qayeeng nambei ingwei a ngo yo, dom na mi zeim qayeeng en moux alis vex. Me qayeeng wei a mi zeim eno mi la bombek, en a se mi wong xeinglala en venaxow qe a mi wong e tiwei wong a lam o wo xeilala. 
\s1 Xel valu mi tul qayeeng en Yesu 
\p  
\v 31 “Wangwei a neil qayeeng wei a maxow o teyei, ond qayeeng wei a neil on se zonghek.  
\v 32 Ekom inyei tambiy nge mi neil qayeeng wei ay yo teyei. Me a woulek bei e xe qayeeng on zonghek. 
\p  
\v 33 “Xam ghe wong xel la wou Yoan me e neil qayeeng wei zonghek o teyei.  
\v 34 A maxow se qou xomaxoneing xe qayeeng, qe a neil en ambei Anutu devind xam.  
\v 35 Yoan on nambei lam wei tum me wo xeiyaing om xam ghe beyal me ghe wo xeimimlala wou xeiyaing sepika. 
\p  
\v 36 “Ekom a xe qayeeng ne eno ghanaw ingwei Yoan o. En xuk dalus wei Mang wong wou ay bei a bong me e ma, eno neil a teyei wou moux alis vex bei Mang wong a lam.  
\v 37 De Mang wei wong a lam eno venaxow tul qayeeng en ay. Ekom xam seng mi ngo e vya o ghe mi wei e ma.  
\v 38 O moxo xe qayeeng wei mi neil eno se dei eivek xam laleimim, en xam seng wongis e tiwei moxo wong e lam o.  
\v 39 Xam ghe mi pyaw qayeeng qes wei yeip eivek xoulek me ghe wou naleimim bei tyek xam a qou mapieing luta luta. Qayeeng ti beimambei yon mi neil a teyei,  
\v 40 ekom xam ghe pesek, en xam ambei seng nam wou ay me na qou mapieing. 
\p  
\v 41 “Ambei se qou lei ngandoung wou xomaxoneing,  
\v 42 ekom a woulek xam. A woulek bei xam seng qou Anutu xe lalei vineing eivek laleimim.  
\v 43 A lam lek Mang lei, eno xam seng qou ay, qe wangwei xel nge nam lek e venaxow lei ond tyek xam a qou e.  
\v 44 Xam ghe mi pamilexe lei ngandoung wei xam ghe mi wong wouma yo de lei ngandoung wei lam wou Anutu venaxow eno xam a bei se qou. Om tyek xam ghe bongis ambei nya? 
\p  
\v 45 “Ekom xam seng bou naleimim bei tyek a byex qayeeng lek xam wou Mang manghalus, qe tambiy wei embei byex qayeeng lek xam eno inyon Mose, tambiy tiwei xam ghe toung mamim wou bei tyek devind xam o.  
\v 46 Wangwei xam ghe bongis Mose on tyek xam ghe bongis ay, en moxo byex qayeeng en ay.  
\v 47 Ekom xam seng wongis qayeeng wei byex o, om nambei nya tyek xam ghe bongis vati wei ambei neil o?” 
\c 6  
\s1 Yesu vet moux 5,000 
\p  
\v 1 Ka bouk valu lak veil en inyon, eno Yesu la lounyeing Galili loxalu nei, inyei lounyeing lei nge eno Taiberias.  
\v 2 De xomaxoneing ngenongakes betiy e me la, en nambei xel yei dee wei lulvako wei wong xel wei vanei eno wo nimzalek o.  
\v 3 Woyom Yesu lek lukendu me la toundei is e xe xel betiyeing.  
\v 4 De Yudayeiw xe bouk ngandoung wei Pasova eno lam paviy. 
\p  
\v 5 Gyeik ingwei Yesu veilma lek me yei xomaxoneing ngenong di lam wou e, eno neil wou Pilip bei, “Tyek xey a bou belet anghei inya me na bong wou xel beimambei ne en xel gya?”  
\v 6 Moxo teling tine en embei daxe Pilip, en moxo wounalei en vati wei embei bong o woy. 
\p  
\v 7 Pilip lewexe wou e bei, “Wangwei xey a bou belet lek malew vaxak yuw on tyek se teyei xel ne titi bei xel gya nayak kaka!” 
\p  
\v 8 Moxo xe betiyeing nge inyon Andrias wei Simon Petele li eno luk bei,  
\v 9 “Yak ti toundei inye eno di qou bali belet nayak lim de woing nayak yayuw, ekom tyek inye devind xomaxoneing ngenong ne nambei nya?” 
\p  
\v 10 Yesu neil embei, “Xam neil wou xomaxoneing on en xel mendei tembuing o.” Qeis ngenong toundei inyon, om xel dei lek. De moux wei dei yon teyei lek ambei 5,000.  
\v 11 Woyom Yesu qou belet me wong dange wou Anutu de wong wou xomaxoneing dalus wei toundei inyon eno xel ya me enden xel. Moxo wong ambei nyon wou woing is. 
\p  
\v 12 Ka xel dalusateiv ya woy, moxo neil wou e xe xel betiyeing bei, “Xam qekuwou myapapu wei toundei yo en kandek ti se nati.”  
\v 13 Om xel qekuwou myapapu wei belet lim wei xel ya de toundei yo me sei eivek pasik xoumeeng yuw me epup. 
\p  
\v 14 Ka xomaxoneing yei dee wei lulvako wei Yesu wong o, eno xel neil embei, “Neing ayang inye Poropet tiwei Anutu neil embei bong e nam lek tembuing o.”  
\v 15 Yesu woulek bei xel embei nam tendu e me embo king wei xel o, om moxo venaxow la veil xel me lox me la lukendu no. 
\s1 Yesu la lek memiing mapu 
\p  
\v 16 Sayeiv la eivek, eno e xe xel betiyeing lep me la xo wei lounyeing nei,  
\v 17 de xel la eivek bot ti me sepa lounyeing me la Kapenaom. Inye bouk, de Yesu se ghei la wou xel.  
\v 18 Laweeng nikanzek ti vei om lounyeing vuklek.  
\v 19 Xel di sepa me la teyei lek kilomita lim o limti, de xel yei Yesu di la lek lounyeing mapu me la paviy xel om xel yaleeng ngandoung.  
\v 20 Ekom moxo neil wou xel bei, “Inye ay yo, om xam seng gwaleeng.”  
\v 21 Woyom xel toung laleind lekti bei qou e me na eivek bot, de lutika eno bot la nenyawes lek beyeeng tiwei xel embei na yo. 
\p  
\v 22 Bouk nge eno moux alis vex nanghei toundei lounyeing nenyawes nge loxalu nei en xel yeimend wou bei bot tixemou di yeip inyei, de Yesu se la is e xe xel betiyeing, qe xel venaxow la.  
\v 23 Woyom xel Taiberias xe bot valu lam paviy beyeeng wei Tambiy Ngandoung wong dange en belet me xel ya yo.  
\v 24 De xel qendu yon yeimend wou bei Yesu lis e xe xel betiyeing se toundei. Om xel la eivek bot ti beimambei yon me la Kapenaom en xel embei na gyimexe Yesu. 
\s1 Yesu e belet wei mapieing o 
\p  
\v 25 Gyeik ingwei xel yeiwou e nanghei lounyeing loxalu nei, eno xel teling e, “Putoung, wang lam inye gyeik inya?” 
\p  
\v 26 Yesu lewexe, “A neil wou xam zonghek, xam seng wimexe ay en ingwei xam ghe wei dee wei lulvako yo, qe en ingwei xam ghe wa belet me e den xam o.  
\v 27 Xam seng bong xuk en lul yaeing wei mi wo nol o, qe en lul yaeing wei emi mendei mapieing luta luta yo, wei Xomaxoneing Neu Moux tyek bong wou xam o. En moxo eno Ma Anutu beyal bei e bong lei ngandoung me bong ambei nyon.” 
\p  
\v 28 Woyom xel teling wou moxo, “Xa bong vati me na bong Anutu xe xuk?” 
\p  
\v 29 Yesu lewexe bei, “Anutu xe xuk eno nambei nye: Xam ghe bongis tambiy tiwei Anutu wong e lam o.” 
\p  
\v 30 Om xel teling wou e, “Tyek wang bong dee wei lulvako vati yo en xa ghei me na bongis wang? Tyek wang bo vati?  
\v 31 Xa bumiyeiw ya mana eivek tembuing bandaing, nambei xel byex eivek xoulek bei, 
\q1 ‘Moxo wong belet wei tyoung gheyapu yo me xel ya.’” \rq Qouloum 16:4\rq* 
\p  
\v 32 Yesu neil wou xel, “A neil wou xam zonghek, inye Mose se wong belet wei tyoung gheyapu eno wou xam, qe Mang wong belet zonghek wei tyoung gheyapu eno wou xam.  
\v 33 En belet wei Anutu xe eno inye e tiwei lam axone nanghei tyoung gheyapu nei me wong mapieing wou xomaxoneing wei tembuing sapa yo.” 
\p  
\v 34 Xel neil embei, “Teiv, wa mi bong belet tiyon wou xa taxombouk.” 
\p  
\v 35 Woyom Yesu neilteyei bei, “A maxow belet wei mapieing o. Xelti embei nam wou ay eno tyek se na maxep, me xelti embei bongis ay eno tyek kwa se tip en memiing.  
\v 36 Ekom nambei a neil wou xam o, xam ghe wei ay ekom xam se ghei wongis.  
\v 37 Xel dalus wei Mang wong wou ay eno tyek nam wou ay, de xelti embei nam wou ay eno tyek a se saing xel.  
\v 38 En a lep me lam anghei tyoung gheyapu nei en ambei se betiwou a maxow xe woueing nalei, qe woueing nalei wei tambiy tiwei wong a lam o.  
\v 39 De lalei vineing wei tambiy tiwei wong a lam eno nambei nye, tyek a se saing xel wei wong wou ay eno ti, qe tyek a piyexe xel lek bouk loxyus.  
\v 40 En Mang xe woueing nalei nambei nye xel eti yeiw wei yei Neu Moux me wongis e eno tyek na qou deing mapieing luta luta, de tyek a piyexe e lek bouk loxyus.” 
\p  
\v 41 Woyom Yudayeiw ngo inyon eno xel luk niseik seik en nambei moxo neil embei, “A belet wei lam axone nanghei tyoung gheyapu yo.”  
\v 42 Xel neil embei, “Beip inye se Yesu Yosep neu wei xey a woulek ma luw ta yo? Nambei nya gweimbeeng neil embei, ‘A lam axone nanghei tyoung gheyapu’?” 
\p  
\v 43 Ekom Yesu neil elox bei, “Xam tip lukeing ngenong on eivek xam venaxow senghoing.  
\v 44 Xelti tyek se nam wou ay qe ka Mang tiwei wong a lam eno na puw e nam le, de tyek a piyexe e qandi lek bouk loxyus.  
\v 45 Qayeeng yeip eivek xoulek wei xel poropet byex o bei, 
\q1 ‘Anutu tyek teyoxe xel.’ \rq Yesaya 54:13\rq* 
\m Xel eti yeiw wei mi ngo Mang me qou kwa wou e eno tyek nam wou ay.  
\v 46 Xelti se yei Mang. Qe e tiwei toundei is Anutu me lam eno emaxow yei Ma.  
\v 47 A neil wou xam zonghek, e tiwei mi wongis eno qou mapieing luta luta.  
\v 48 A maxow belet wei mapieing o.  
\v 49 Xam bumimyeiw ya mana eivek tembuing bandaing, ekom xel mey.  
\v 50 Ekom inye belet wei lam axone nanghei tyoung gheyapu, bei xomaxoneing gya dom xel se mey.  
\v 51 A maxow belet wei mapieing wei lam axone nanghei tyoung gheyapu yo. Wangwei xelti embei gya belet tine, on tyek mendei mapieing luta luta. Belet tine inye a leyeis, wei tyek a bong bei embong mapieing wou xomaxoneing wei tembuing sapa yo.” 
\p  
\v 52 Woyom Yudayeiw di pyalek ama eivek xel venaxow senghoing me neil, “Nambei nya tambiy tine tyek bong emaxow leyeis me xey a gha?” 
\p  
\v 53 Yesu neil wou xel, “A neil wou xam zonghek, wangwei xam ambei seng gwa Xomaxoneing Neu Moux leyeis me na num e gyand ond xam seng qou mapieing eivek xow.  
\v 54 Xelti embei gya a leyeis me na num a gyand on tyek na qou mapieing luta luta, de tyek a piyexe e lek bouk loxyus.  
\v 55 En a leyeis on yaeing zonghek me a gyand on numeing zonghek.  
\v 56 Xelti embei gya a leyeis me na num a gyand yond mindei eivek ay de a mindei eivek e.  
\v 57 Nambei ingwei Mang wei mapieing eno wong a lam me a toundei mapieing en Mang, om xelti embei gya a leyeis on tyek mendei mapieing en ay.  
\v 58 Tine inye belet wei lam axone nanghei tyoung gheyapu nei yo. Xam bumimyeiw ya mana de mey, ekom xelti embei gya belet tine ond tyek mendei mapieing luta luta.”  
\v 59 Yesu neil lul tine gyeik ingwei di teyoxe xel eivek xomek qekueing ama nanghei Kapenaom o. 
\s1 Xel betiyeing ngenong la veil Yesu 
\p  
\v 60 Xel ngo inyon de e xe xel betiyeing ngenong neil, “Teyoxeing on wo nimaying. Eti tyek na zeimaxoun inyon?” 
\p  
\v 61 Yesu woulek bei e xe xel betiyeing di luk ngenong en tine, om Yesu neil wou xel, “Qayeeng tine wo nol wou xam laleimim?  
\v 62 Wangwei xam ghe gwei ingwei Xomaxoneing Neu Moux nox me na tyoung gheyapu wei mindei takwei yo on tyek xam ghe bou naleimim ambei nya?  
\v 63 Laweeng mi wong mapieing wou moux alis vex. Xe neing se teyei bei devind xey. Qayeeng beimambei wei a neil wou xam eno inyon laweeng me xel on mapieing.  
\v 64 Ekom xam valu seng wongis.” En myaxeeng eno Yesu woulek e tiwei se wongis o me tyek na toung e na eivek xel ba memend o.  
\v 65 Moxo tetulexe me neil embei, “Inye vati wei a neil wou xam bei xelti se teyei bei nam wou ay, qe ka Mang bo nikanzek wou e le.” 
\p  
\v 66 Lek bouk tiyon eno e xe xel betiyeing ngenongakes pekwi me lox me la de xel se betiwou e no. 
\p  
\v 67 Yesu teling wou e xe xel betiyeing xoumeeng yuw on bei, “Xam is xam ambeing na veil ay?” 
\p  
\v 68 Simon Petele lewexe wou e, “Tambiy Ngandoung, tyek xa na wou eti? Wa xe qayeeng on mi wo mapieing luta luta.  
\v 69 Xa wongis me na woulek bei wang on Vambuing tiwei Anutu yo.” 
\p  
\v 70 Woyom Yesu neil elox bei, “A beyal xam xoumeeng yuw. Ekom xam on ti eno laweeng nol!”  
\v 71 Moxo neil inyon en Yudas wei Simon Iskariot neu moux o, inyon xel xoumeeng yuw eno ti, wei tyek na neil e teyei me na toung e na eivek xel ba memend o. 
\c 7  
\s1 Yesu la Bouk ngandoung wei Xomek Laweeng o 
\p  
\v 1 Ka tine la veil eno Yesu la di ghavineeng eivek Galili, en embei se nox Yudia en Yudayeiw embei nyeis e mey.  
\v 2 Ekom gyeik ingwei xel Yudayeiw xe Bouk ngandoung wei Xomek Laweeng eno paviy,  
\v 3 om Yesu liyeiw neil wou e, “Wang na veil Galili me ghe na Yudia, en kandek wa xe xel betiyeing gyei lulvako wei wa being bong o.  
\v 4 Wangwei xelti embei xomaxoneing boulek bei e lei ngandoung on se mi wong xuk eivek xupekeing. Wangwei wa being bong lulti beimambei yon, ond wa talex xow wou xomaxoneing wei tembuing sapa nei.”  
\v 5 Embong emaxow liyeiw le, ekom xel se wongis e. 
\p  
\v 6 Nambei nyon Yesu neil wou xel, “A xe bouk se ghei lam, qe bouk dalus ne eno inye xam xe bouk nimza.  
\v 7 Xel xomaxoneing wei tembuing ne eno se teyei bei bo nol wou xam, qe xel mi wo nol wou ay en a mi neil kwa nilul wei xel mi wong o teyei.  
\v 8 Xam ghe na Bouk ngandoung on. Dom tyek a se zek me nana Bouk ngandoung tiyon, en nambei a xe bouk se ghei lam.”  
\v 9 Ka neil ambei nyon wou xel woy, dom toundei Galili. 
\p  
\v 10 Ka liyeiw la Bouk ngandoung veil, om moxo la is ambei nyon, se la yanyateiv, qe la xupekeing.  
\v 11 De eivek Bouk ngandoung eno teivateiv wei Yudayeiw toundei me di yei e teyei teyei me teling bei, “Tambiy tiwei yo inya?” 
\p  
\v 12 Eivek xel wei qekuma yon senghoing eno xel di ngoung lumama wouma me luk en moxo. Xel valu neil embei, “Moxo nimza.” De xel valu neil elox bei, “ Ma, tambiy on mi tyoxe xomaxoneing.” 
\p  
\v 13 Ekom xelti se neil lulti yeip yaing lek moxo en xel yaleeng en teivateiv wei Yudayeiw o. 
\s1 Yesu teyoxe xel nanghei ingwei Bouk ngandoung nei 
\p  
\v 14 Eivek bouk senghoing wei Bouk ngandoung eno Yesu lek me la eivek tete lalei wei xomek vambuing o me di teyoxe moux alis vex.  
\v 15 De Yudayeiw etek me teling bei, “Tambiy nei qou lupeyei nei nambei nya moxo se wevek ti?” 
\p  
\v 16 Yesu lewexe, “A xe teyoxeing ne inye se a maxow xe. Qe inye lam wou tiwei wong a lam o.  
\v 17 Wangwei xelti beyal bei bong e teyei lek Anutu lalei ond tyek gyei bei teyoxeing wei a ne lam wou Anutu, o a di neil angya a maxow kwang.  
\v 18 Xelti embei neil qayeeng angya emaxow xe kwa ond inyon mi sanghoxe xow, ekom xelti embei bong xuk me sanghoxe tiwei wong e lam o lei, ond inyon tambiy wei zonghek o. De tyonyeing ma veil e.  
\v 19 Beip Mose se wong petieing wou xam? Ekom xam ti seng mi betiwou. Nambei nya xam a being nyeis a mey?” 
\p  
\v 20 Xel wei qekuma yon lewexe bei, Memo ti nale eivek wang. “Eti embei nyeis wang?” 
\p  
\v 21 Yesu neil wou xel, “A wong lulvako ti eno xam dalus ghe etek.  
\v 22 Mose wong kwa wei ghuweing ninavi yo, ekom inyon Mose venaxow se wong kwa yon qe inyon lam wou xe bundyeiw, om xam ghe mi ghuw yak ninavi lek bouk wei Sabat o.  
\v 23 Wangwei xam ambei mi ghuw yakyeis ninavi lek bouk wei Sabat o en kandek xam se pyalek Mose xe petieing, on nambei nya xam laleimim mi wo vanei wou ay en ingwei ambei bong tambiy ti bo nimzalek Sabat o?  
\v 24 Xam a tip pepyawexeing lul wei xam a being gwei nangya mamim o, de xam pepyawexe en sakwaing bombek.” 
\s1 Xel pyalek ama bei Yesu yon eti? 
\p  
\v 25 En qes tiyon xomaxoneing valu wei Yerusalem nei teling, “Beip inyei tambiy tiwei xel embei nyeis e mey o?  
\v 26 Inye moxo di luk wou xel yanyateiv me xel di yei me ngo e ekom xelti se nale zeyi e, en beip xel gyovaxa woulek neing bei e Kilisi?  
\v 27 Ekom xey a woulek ingwei tambiy tine lam anghei yo, de gyeik ingwei Kilisi embei nam eno tyek xelti se boulek ingwei lam anghei yo.” 
\p  
\v 28 Woyom Yesu nanghei di teyoxe xel eivek tete lalei wei xomek vambuing o, me taxe bei, “Ee, xam ghe woulek ay, me xam ghe woulek ingwei a lam anghei yo? A se lam inye nangya a venaxow xe woueing nalei, qe tambiy tiwei wong a lam eno inye zonghek. De xam seng woulek e,  
\v 29 ekom a woulek e en nambei a lam anghei ingwei e toundei nei de moxo wong a lam.” 
\p  
\v 30 Gyeik ingwei Yesu neil tiyon eno xel di wong me yei en xel embei zeimaxoun moxo, ekom xelti se ax mema lek e en nambei moxo xe bouk se ghei lam.  
\v 31 Moux alis vex ngenong wei toundei eivek qekueing ama yon eno wongis Yesu. Xel neil embei, “Gyeik ingwei Kilisi embei nam eno tyek bong dee wei lulvako yo ngenong ghanaw tambiy tine?” 
\p  
\v 32 De xel Parisi ngo ingwei moux alis vex di ngoung wouma en lul wei e wong o. Woyom xel lumuki leitata yo me xel Parisi wong xel belimbo wei mi yeiteyei xomek vambuing eno la en xel embei na zeimaxoun e. 
\p  
\v 33 Yesu neil embei, “Tyek a toumendei bouk sepika is xam, dekakom nana wou tambiy tiwei wong a lam o.  
\v 34 Tyek xam ghe gwimexe ay, ekom tyek xam seng gweiwou ay, me ingwei a la toundei nei, eno xam seng teyei being nam.” 
\p  
\v 35 De Yudayeiw di neil wouma bei, “Tambiy tine tyek na inya me xe se ghei e? Tyek moxo na wou xel wei xey o, wei xel mindei lala eivek xel Grik senghoing o me teyoxe xel Grik?  
\v 36 Moxo neil tine en qes ambei nya gyeik ingwei e neil embei, ‘Tyek xam ghe gwimexe ay ekom tyek xam seng gweiwou ay,’ me ‘Ingwei a la toundei nei, eno tyek xam seng nam?’” 
\p  
\v 37 Lek bouk ngandoung tiwei yus o, eno Yesu nale me taxe bei, “Wangwei xelti kwa tip en memiing ond wong e lam wou ay me num.  
\v 38 Xelti embei bongis ay nambei Xoulek neil o, on tyek memiing veleivlei wei mapieing eno mendi na eivek e lalei me qapyex me na.”  
\v 39 Ekom neil en Laweeng wei xelti embei bongis e eno tyek na qou yo. De ela tyip bouk tine eno Laweeng seng ghei lam, en Yesu seng ghei wo lei ngandoung. 
\p  
\v 40 Xel ngo e xe qayeeng tiyon, eno xomaxoneing valu neil embei, “Neing ayang tambiy tiyon Poropet.” 
\p  
\v 41 De xel valu neil embei, “Moxo Kilisi.” 
\p De xel valu teling bei, “Nambei nya Kilisi tyek nam anghei Galili?  
\v 42 Beip xoulek se neil embei Kilisi tyek nam eivek Dawit neumambu me nam anghei Betelem, beyeeng wei Dawit mindei lek o?”  
\v 43 En nambei Yesu om xomaxoneing dembuma.  
\v 44 Xel valu embei zeimaxoun e, ekom xelti se ax mema lek moxo. 
\s1 Yudayeiw xe gyovaxa se wongis Yesu 
\p  
\v 45 Se denlek en xel belimbo wei xomek vambuing o lox me la wou xel lumuki leitata yo me Parisiyeiw, xel teling wou xel, “Nambei nya xam seng qou e me ghe lam lalei?” 
\p  
\v 46 Xel belimbo neilteyei bei, “Xelti se mi neil qayeeng ambei tambiy tine.” 
\p  
\v 47 Xel Parisi neil wou xel bei, “Moxo tyoxe xam is ambei nyon?  
\v 48 Beip xam ghe wei bei xel gyovaxa me xel Parisi ti wongis e?  
\v 49 Ma! Ekom xel qendu tiyon se woulek lulti eivek petieing. Om tyek Anutu bong myaveweeng wou xel.” 
\p  
\v 50 Nikodimas, tambiy tiwei la wou Yesu takwei eno inyon ingwei xel o ti, om teling,  
\v 51 “Beip petieing wei xey o neil embei xey a bo qayeeng en xelti bandaing? Ma, myaxeeng eno xey a ngo e xe qayeeng me na ghei bei e wong vati?” 
\p  
\v 52 Xel neil elox bei, “Wang on Galili is? Wimexe e wo nimza eivek Anutu xe qapiya me wei, Poropet ti tyek se nam eivek Galili.” 
\s1 Xel qou vex wei wo kwa pesiv o ti me la wou Yesu\f + \fr 7:53-8:11 \ft Xel wei lupeyei eno neil embei Yoan se byex, qe tambiy nge byex. \f* 
\p  
\v 53 Woyom xel titi lox me la bend bend. 
\c 8  
\nb  
\v 1 Ekom Yesu la lukendu Oliv.  
\v 2 Ka satiboukeing lul eno moxo lox me la tete lalei wei xomek vambuing o no, me xomaxoneing qekuma vivekwou e, de moxo dei me di teyoxe xel.  
\v 3 De xel putoung wei petieing o me xel Parisi yei vex wei mi wong kwapesiv o ti me qou me lam. Xel wong vexo nale wou xomaxoneing wei toundei eivek qendu yon mend  
\v 4 me neil wou Yesu, “Putoung, xa xei vex tine wo kwapesiv.  
\v 5 Eivek petieing eno Mose neil embei xey a banex vex ambei nye en qakous me e mey. Wambei neil vati?”  
\v 6 Xel wong telinyeing tiyon wou e nambei lepulek, en xel di yimexe qes wei xel embei bong qayeeng en e yo. 
\p Ekom Yesu dundek me di byex lek tembuing en mema deyis.  
\v 7 Xel di embek teling e ngenong om moxo nale ghey me neil wou xel, “Wangwei xelti se mi bong sewokeing nei ond e banex vexo en qakous atax.”  
\v 8 Moxo lox me la dundek no me di byex lek tembuing. 
\p  
\v 9 Xel ngo qayeeng on eno xel titi la veil inyon xel wei vakovek qes ngenong eno la tax de xel valu la yus. Dom Yesu venaxow toundei de vex on toukale inyon.  
\v 10 Yesu nale ghey me teling wou vexo bei, “Vex, xel la inya? Beip xelti se toundei bei bo qayeeng en wang?” 
\p  
\v 11 Vexo neil embei, “Ma, teiv, xelti se toundei.” 
\p Woyom Yesu neilteyei bei, “Ay is ambei nyon a se wo qayeeng en wang. La de wa seng nox me na bong sewokeing no.” 
\s1 Yesu e xeiyaing wei tembuing o 
\p  
\v 12 Yesu lox me la luk wou xomaxoneing no, eno moxo neil embei, “A xeiyaing wei tembuing o. Xelti embei betiwou ay eno tyek se teyei bei na eivek mapetok, qe tyek na qou xeiyaing wei mapieing o.” 
\p  
\v 13 Xel Parisi neil wou moxo bei, “Wang mi neil xuk me kwa wei wamaxow o teyei, om qayeeng wei wang on se neing.” 
\p  
\v 14 Yesu lewexe bei, “Ee, a neil lulti beimambei ne lek venaxow, a xe qayeeng ne neing, en a woulek ingwei a lam anghei yo de ingwei ambei na yo. Ekom xam seng woulek ingwei a lam anghei yo me ingwei ambei na yo.  
\v 15 Xam ghe mi wo qayeeng en kwa wei xomaxoneing o, a se mi wo qayeeng en xelti.  
\v 16 Ekom wangwei ambei bo qayeeng en xelti, ond a xe qayeeng on zonghek, en nambei se a maxow, qe a mi nale is Mang, tiwei wong a lam o.  
\v 17 Eivek xam venaxow xe petieing eno xel byex ambei nye, wangwei tambiy yayuw embei neil qayeeng teyeima ond luw xe qayeeng on zonghek.  
\v 18 A maxow a mi neil qayeeng en venaxow, de tiwei mi yeimawou yo eno inye Mang tiwei wong a lam o.” 
\p  
\v 19 Woyom xel teling moxo, “Wa mam inya?” 
\p Yesu neil elox bei, “Xam seng woulek a Mang. Wangwei xam ghe boulek ay on tyek xam ghe boulek Mang is ambei nyon.” 
\p  
\v 20 Moxo neil qayeeng tine gyeik di teyoxe xel eivek tete lalei wei xomek vambuing o paviy ingwei xel mi toung da eivek o. Ekom xelti se zeimaxoun e en nambei e xe bouk seng ghei lam. 
\s1 Yesu neil embei tyek xam seng nam ingwei ambei na yo 
\p  
\v 21 Yesu neil no wou xel, “A la, dom tyek xam seng gwei ay, de tyek xam amey eivek sewokeing wei xam o. De ingwei ambei na nei eno tyek xam seng nam.” 
\p  
\v 22 Qayeeng tiyon wong Yudayeiw teling wouma bei, “Tyek moxo nyeis venaxow amey? Om neil embei, ‘Ingwei ambei na eno xam seng teyei bei nam’?” 
\p  
\v 23 Ekom Yesu tetulexe bei, “Xam on anghei nge xone de ay anghei nge gheyapu. Xam anghei tembuing de a se nanghei tembuing ne.  
\v 24 A neil wou xam woy bei tyek xam amey eivek xam xe sewokeing, wangwei xam seng bongis bei A Maxow Mindei Bei Nye, on tyek xam amey eivek sewokeing wei xam o.” 
\p  
\v 25 Xel teling, “Wang eti?” 
\p Yesu neil elox bei, “Kayon a neil wou xam myaxeeng eno.  
\v 26 A xe qayeeng ngenong di yeip en ingwei ambei neil me na bong qayeeng en xam o. Ekom tambiy tiwei wong a lam eno e xe kwa yon zonghek, yom vati wei a ngo wou e eno a neil wou xomaxoneing wei tembuing sapa yo.” 
\p  
\v 27 Xel se woulek ingwei Yesu di neil wou xel en Ma yo.  
\v 28 Om Yesu neil embei, “Gyeik ingwei xam a zeim Xomaxoneing Neu Moux zekna, woyom tyek xam ghe boulek bei A maxow a mindei bei nye de a se mi wong lulti nangya kwang, qe a mi neil qayeeng nambei kawei Mang teyoxe wou ay yo.  
\v 29 Tambiy tiwei wong a lam eno mindei is ay, moxo se mi saing ay de a maxow a mindei, en a mi wong vatiyeiw wei e lalei vind o.”  
\v 30 Xomaxoneing ngo ingwei moxo neil ambei nyon, eno xel ngenong wongis e. 
\s1 Apraham neuyeiw la vevopeing 
\p  
\v 31 Yesu neil wou Yudayeiw wei wongis e yo bei, “Wangwei xam a zeimaxoun a xe qayeeng teyoxeing, ond neing ayang xam on a xe betiyeing.  
\v 32 Woyom tyek xam ghe boulek qayeeng zonghek, de qayeeng zonghek na tul xam ghe na nivax.” 
\p  
\v 33 Xel lewexe lek e bei, “Xa ne Apraham neumambu, xa se xukxe bandaing wei xelti yo. Nambei nya wang neimbei tyek xa na nivax?” 
\p  
\v 34 Yesu neil elox bei, “A neil zonghek wou xam, xel sapa wei mi wong sewokeing eno xel on xukxe bandaing wei sewokeing o.  
\v 35 Xukxe bandaing ti se mindei is mamata me neuyeiw takwei takwei qe neu mindei takwei takwei.  
\v 36 Om wangwei Neu Moux na tul xam ghe na nivax, ond xam ghe la nivax zonghek.  
\v 37 A woulek bei xam on velei wei Apraham o, ekom xam a being nyeis a mey, en nambei a xe qayeeng se yeip eivek xam laleimim.  
\v 38 A mi neil wou xam en vati wei a xei lam wou Mang o, de xam ghe mi wong vati wei xam ghe ngo wou xam mamim.” 
\p  
\v 39 Xel lewexe bei, “Apraham on xa mami.” 
\p Yesu neil embei, “Wangwei Apraham neuyeiw xam, woyom tyek xam ghe bong lul wei Apraham mi wong o.  
\v 40 A tambiy tiwei a mi neil qayeeng zonghek wei a ngo wou Anutu yo, ekom xam a being nyeis a mey. Apraham se mi wong kwa nambei nyon.  
\v 41 Xam ghe mi wong lulul wei xam venaxow mamim mi wong o.” 
\p Xel neil embei, “Xa tamiyeiw se wo kwapesiv me wou xa ti, qe Mang tixemou wei xa xe eno Anutu venaxow.” 
\p  
\v 42 Yesu neil wou xel, “Wangwei Anutu yon xam Mamim, on tyek xam laleimim devind ay, en a toundei is Anutu me na lam. A lam inye. A se lam angya a maxow kwang, qe moxo wong a lam.  
\v 43 Nambei nya a xe qayeeng se yeip yaing wou xam? En qes ambei nye xam seng teyei bei ngo vati wei a neil o.  
\v 44 Xam mamim on Sandang, me xam ambei mi bong kwa wei xam mamim mi wong o. Myaxeeng eno moxo mi leis xel mey, se mi zeim qayeeng zonghek, en inyei qayeeng zonghek se toundei eivek e. De mi neil qayeeng tyonyeing en inyon emaxow tyonyeing qes, en moxo tyonyeingana me wo ma en tyonyeing.  
\v 45 En nambei a mi neil qayeeng zonghek, ekom xam seng mi wongis ay!  
\v 46 Xel wei xam on valu yei bei a wong sewokeing? Wangwei a mi neil qayeeng zonghek, ond nambei nya xam seng wongis ay?  
\v 47 Tambiy tiwei Anutu xe eno mi ngo vati wei Anutu mi neil o. Xam on Anutu se xe en qes bei xam seng mi ngo vati wei e mi neil o.” 
\s1 Yesu lei ngandoung ghanaw Apraham 
\p  
\v 48 Yudayeiw lewexe wou moxo bei, “Xa neil neing en ingwei xa neimbei wa Samaria ti om memo ti nale eivek wang?” 
\p  
\v 49 Yesu neil embei, “Memo ti se toungale eivek ay ti, qe a mi sanghoxe mang lei de xam ghe mi beoux ay.  
\v 50 A se di ximexe lei ngandoung wei a maxow o. Qe inyei xelti di yimexe, de moxo inye tambiy wei mi ngo qayeeng o.  
\v 51 Neing ayang a neil wou xam, wangwei xelti embei betiwou a xe qayeeng on tyek se teyei bei daxe meyeing.” 
\p  
\v 52 En tiyon eno xel Yudayeiw neil embei, “Gweimbeeng xa woulek bei memo dei eivek wang! Apraham mey me xel poropet is ambei nyon, de wang neimbei xelti embei betiwou wa xe qayeeng on tyek se teyei bei daxe meyeing.  
\v 53 Wang ghanaw xe mend Apraham? Moxo mey, me xel poropet is. Wang wou naleim bei wang eti?” 
\p  
\v 54 Yesu neil elox bei, “Wangwei a sanghoxe a maxow leing ond a leing on bandaing. Mang tiwei xam ghe neimbei xam xe Anutu eno mi sanghoxe a leing.  
\v 55 Xam seng woulek e, qe a woulek e. Wangwei a neimbei a se woulek e on a wo tyonyeing ambei xam, ekom a woulek e me na mi betiwou e xe qayeeng.  
\v 56 Xam bumim Apraham wo xeilala en embei gyei a xe bouk, moxo yei woy de wo xeilala.” 
\p  
\v 57 Yudayeiw neil wou moxo bei, “Wa xe vakovek qes se ghei la 50, de wang wei Apraham!” 
\p  
\v 58 Yesu lewexe bei, “A neil wou xam zonghek, takwei wei Apraham se ghei umbek eno A Maxow A Mindei.”  
\v 59 Woyom xel qou qakous en xel embei banex e, ekom Yesu xupek en xel me la myayaing veil tete wei xomek vambuing o. 
\c 9  
\s1 Pavulek wei moux matekeing ti yo 
\p  
\v 1 Ka moxo di la, eno moxo yei moux ti matek gyeik umbek o.  
\v 2 Moxo xe xel betiyeing teling e, “Putoung, eti wong sewokeing, moux tine venaxow o ma luw ta, om ingwei matek gyeik umbek o?” 
\p  
\v 3 Yesu neil embei, “Moux tine se wong sewokeing o ma luw ta se wo sewokeing, qe lul tine qandi bei Anutu xe xuk e gyeip yaing eivek e xe mapieing.  
\v 4 Kawei bendiyeing ne eno xey a bong xuk wou tambiy tiwei wong a lam o. De boukeing nam eno xelti tyek se bong xuk.  
\v 5 Gyeik ingwei a toundei eivek tembuing sapa ne, eno a maxow xeiyaing wei tembuing sapa yo.” 
\p  
\v 6 Yesu neil ambei nyon, dom pesuv myalouk lek tembuing me wong e wo bandis de toung lek moux tiyon manghalus.  
\v 7 Moxo neil wou e, “La, wang na zipek eivek lounyeing wei Siloam nei” (qayeeng tiyon qes ambei inye wong e la). Om moux tiyon la lipek, de loum beeng eno manghalus yeila. 
\p  
\v 8 Moxo xe xel wei e beeng qes o me xel wei yei e takwei gyeik e mindei me tay lulul eno teling bei, “Beip inyei tambiy tiwei mindei me tay lulul o?”  
\v 9 Xel valu neil embei e inyon. 
\p De xel valu neil embei, “Ma, inye xel nge ekom ma nambei e.” 
\p Ekom moxo venaxow neil xow teyei bei, “Inye ay yo.” 
\p  
\v 10 Xel teling e, “Woyom nambei nya wa mamghalus yeila?” 
\p  
\v 11 Moxo neil elox bei, “Tambiy tiwei xel mi neil Yesu eno wong tembuing wo bandis me toung lek a mang. Moxo neil wou ay bei a na zipek anghei Siloam. Om a la lipek, de woyom a mang yeila.” 
\p  
\v 12 Xel teling e bei, “Moux tiyon inya?” 
\p Moxo neil embei, “A se woulek.” 
\s1 Xel Parisi teling moux tiwei ma yeila yo 
\p  
\v 13 Xel qou moux tiwei matekeing eno me la wou xel Parisi.  
\v 14 Bouk tiwei Yesu wong tembuing wo bandis me vindek moux tiyon malek eno inyon Sabat.  
\v 15 Om nambei nyon xel Parisi teling wou e no bei, “Nambei nya wa mam yeila?” Om moxo neil elox, “Moxo toung bandis lek a mang, me a lipek de gweimbeeng a mang yeila.” 
\p  
\v 16 Xel Parisi valu neil embei, “Tambiy tine se lam wou Anutu, en se betiwou petieing wei Sabat o.” 
\p Ekom xel valu teling, “Nambei nya xel wei sewokeing o tyek bong dee wei lulvako yo nambei nye?” Om xel dembuma. 
\p  
\v 17 Se denlek en xel pekwi mend wou moux matekeing on no, “Wambei neil ambei nya en e en ingwei wong wa mam yeila yo?” 
\p Moux tiyon neil elox bei, “Moxo poropet ti.” 
\p  
\v 18 Yudayeiw se ghei wongis bei moxo matek me mavindek lek, deka xel wo qayeeng la wou moux on ma luw ta wole.  
\v 19 Luw lam de xel teling wou luw, “Inye muw neumim? Inye tambiy tine muw ghe neimbei e matek gyeik umbek o? Nambei nya gweimbeeng e manghalus yeila?” 
\p  
\v 20 Ma luw ta lewexe bei, “Uw a woulek bei inye uw neumi, me uw a woulek bei umbek matekeing.  
\v 21 Ekom e yeila gweimbeeng ne nambei nya, o eti wong e ma yeila eno uw se woulek. Xam teling wou e. Moxo wo teiv om tyek na neil xow teyei.”  
\v 22 Moxo ma luw ta neil ambei nyon en luw yaleeng en Yudayeiw, en xel Yudayeiw tup qayeeng bei xelti embei neimbei Yesu e Kilisi, on tyek xel a tiy e veil xomek qekueing ama.  
\v 23 Inyon qes tiyon om ma luw ta neil embei, “Moxo wo teiv, om xam teling wou e.” 
\p  
\v 24 Om luyuw eno xel taxe moux tiwei matekeing o me neil wou, “Wa sanghoxe Anutu, en xa woulek bei tambiy tiyon mi wong sewokeing.” 
\p  
\v 25 Moxo neil elox bei, “Beip e mi wo sewokeing o ma, a se woulek. A woulek lulti bei a mang tek ekom gweimbeeng a mang yeila!” 
\p  
\v 26 Woyom xel teling wou e, “Moxo wong ambei nya wou wang? E wong wa mam yeila nambei nya?” 
\p  
\v 27 Moxo lewexe bei, “A neil wou xam woy ekom xam seng ngo. Nambei nya xam ambei ngo no? Xam a being bong ambei e xe betiyeing is?” 
\p  
\v 28 Woyom xel wo vyend wou e me neil embei, “Wang on tambiy tiyon xe betiyeing! De xa ne betiyeing wei Mose yo!  
\v 29 Xa woulek bei Anutu luk is Mose, ekom en tambiy tiyon, eno xa se woulek bei e lam anghei inya.” 
\p  
\v 30 De moux on lewexe bei, “Gweimbeeng xam ghe neil qayeeng on nelu ti! Xam seng woulek ingwei e lam anghei yo, qe moxo wong a mang yeila.  
\v 31 Xey a woulek bei Anutu se mi ngo xel wei sewokeing o. Qe moxo mi ngo xel wei mi wo lalo wou e me betiwou e yo.  
\v 32 Xelti se mi ngo ka bei, xelti wong tambiy wei umbek matekeing eno ma yeila.  
\v 33 Wangwei Anutu se bong tambiy tiyon nam, on tyek se bong lulti.” 
\p  
\v 34 Xel neil elox bei, “Sewokeing pup wang gyeik wang umbek o, wambei teyoxe xa!” De xel tiy moxo la. 
\s1 Xel wei se wongis eno mend tek 
\p  
\v 35 Yesu ngo bei xel tiy e, de gyeik ingwei moxo yei e, eno neil wou bei, “Wang wongis Xomaxoneing Neu Moux?” 
\p  
\v 36 Moux on teling bei, “Teiv, tambiy tiyon eti? Wa neil wou ay en a bongis e yo.” 
\p  
\v 37 Yesu neil embei, “Gweimbeeng wang wei e, inye tambiy tiwei di luk is wang ne.” 
\p  
\v 38 Woyom moux on neil embei, “Tambiy Ngandoung, a wongis o,” de moxo wo lalo wou Yesu. 
\p  
\v 39 Yesu neil embei, “A lam eivek tembuing tine en qayeeng wongeing, en kandek xel wei mend tekeing eno gyeina de eti yeiw wei mend yeila eno tyek bo mend tekeing.” 
\p  
\v 40 Xel Parisi valu wei toundei is e eno ngo ingwei e neil ambei nyon om xel teling, “Vati? Wambei xa mami tek is?” 
\p  
\v 41 Yesu neil embei, “Wangwei xam mamim atek, on sewokeing ma veil xam, ekom xam ghe mi neimbei xam mamim yeila, om sewokeing nanghei di yeip wou xam.” 
\c 10  
\s1 Gyovaxa me e xe sipsip 
\p  
\v 1 Yesu neil embei, “A neil wou xam zonghek, moux wei se la lox tete mya wei sipsip, qe lek wou tete nanghei ba nei me la lalei eno inyon panaxana me tambiy wei mi wo nol wou xel o.  
\v 2 De moux wei mi la lox tete mya eno inyon gyovaxa wei e xe sipsip o.  
\v 3 De tambiy tiwei mi yei tete mya teyei eno tax veil moxo, me sipsip mi ngo e vya. Moxo mi taxe e xe sipsip titi leind de mi dandiy xel me la myayaing.  
\v 4 Ka moxo qou e xe sipsip dalus me la myayaing, eno moxo mi la tax en xel, de e xe sipsip mi betiwou e en nambei xel woulek e vya.  
\v 5 Ekom xel se mi betiwou xel bange, xel mi pek en e en nambei xel se woulek xel bange vya.”  
\v 6 Yesu neil qayeeng pakeing tiyon wou xel, ekom xel se woulek vati wei moxo di neil wou xel o. 
\p  
\v 7 Dekalekom Yesu neil no, “A neil wou xam zonghek, a tete mya wei sipsip o.  
\v 8 Xel dalus wei lam a tax en ay eno panaxana me mi wo nol wou xel, ekom sipsip se mi ngo xel.  
\v 9 A tete mya, wangwei xelti embei nam wou ay me na eivek tete lalei on tyek Anutu devind e. Moxo tyek nam eivek lalei de doukna myayaing, me na qou lulul yaeing.  
\v 10 Panaxana mi lam en panaxeing tixemou me leiseing xel a mey me mi wo nol wou, ekom a lam bei xel a qou mapieing, me mapieing e pup xel. 
\p  
\v 11 “A maxow gyovaxa nimza wei sipsip o. Gyovaxa nimza wei sipsip eno mi saing e xe mapieing en sipsip.  
\v 12 De xukxe wei xel mi xouv e me e mi yeiteyei sipsip eno se gyovaxa wei wo ma en sipsip o, om gyeik ingwei yei naw bemeeng lam, eno saing sipsip de pek la. Woyom naw bemeeng nga sipsip de tiy xel vula.  
\v 13 De moux tiyon pek me la en nambei xel mi xouv en malew om se wounalei ngenong en sipsip. 
\p  
\v 14 “A maxow gyovaxa nimza wei sipsip o, a woulek a xe sipsip de a xe sipsip woulek ay,  
\v 15 nambei kawei Mang woulek ay de a woulek Mang. Me a saing a xe mapieing en sipsip.  
\v 16 A xe sipsip valu wei xel se mi nale eivek tete ne. Om a na qou xel me na nam is ambei nyon. De tyek xel a ngo a vyang is ambei nyon, me tyek xel bo sipsip qendu tixemou me gyovaxa wei sipsip o tixemou.  
\v 17 En qes tine om Mang lalei vind ay bei a saing a xe mapieing de na qou enoum no.  
\v 18 Xelti se zeim a xe mapieing veil ay, qe a maxow a zeim a xe mapieing veil. A ningkanzek teyei bei na zeim mapieing wei ay yo veil, de a ningkanzek teyei bei na qou enoum no. En Mang peti wou ay ambei nyon bei a bong.” 
\p  
\v 19 Lek qayeeng ti beimambei ne eno wong Yudayeiw dembuma no.  
\v 20 Xel ngenong neil embei, “Moxo memo nale eivek e me e wo bandol. Xam ambei ngo e enva?” 
\p  
\v 21 Ekom xel valu neil embei, “Inyei se qayeeng wei tambiy wei memo nale eivek o. Memo ti teyei lek bei bong xel wei matekeing o gyeina?” 
\s1 Xel Yudayeiw se wongis 
\p  
\v 22 Woyom bouk ngandoung wei lalo eno lam tyip en ingwei xel mi wou naleind en xomek vambuing wei xel wong wou Anutu nanghei Yerusalem o. Inyon bouk wei nityuweing o,  
\v 23 de Yesu toundei eivek tete lalei wei xomek vambuing o me la di ghavineeng lek zek wei Salomo lei lek o.  
\v 24 De Yudayeiw lam nale vivekwou e, me neil embei, “Gyeik inya wa neil xow teyei? Wangwei bei inyon wa Kilisi, neilteyei wou xa.” 
\p  
\v 25 Yesu lewexe bei, “A neil wou xam woy, ekom xam seng wongis. De xuk wei a wong lek Mang lei eno neil a teyei,  
\v 26 ekom xam seng wongis en nambei xam on a se xe sipsip.  
\v 27 A xe sipsip mi ngo a vyang, me a woulek xel, de xel mi betiwou ay.  
\v 28 A wong deing mapieing luta luta wou xel, me tyek xel se teyei bei mey, de xelti tyek se tetei xel veil a memang.  
\v 29 Mang wei wong xel wou ay eno nikanzek ghanaw xel dalus, xelti tyek se tetei xel veil Mang mema.  
\v 30 Ay me Mang eno uw xouing tixemou.” 
\p  
\v 31 Xel Yudayeiw lox me la balu qakous no en xel embei banex e,  
\v 32 ekom Yesu neil wou xel, “A talex xuk nimza ngenong wei Mang o wou xam. En lul tina eno xam ambei banex ay en qakous?” 
\p  
\v 33 Xel Yudayeiw neil elox bei, “Xa bei se banex wang en qakous en xuk nimza wei wang wong on, qe en ingwei wang lukyak lek Anutu, en nambei wa xomaxoneing bandaing, ekom wang neimbei wa Anutu.” 
\p  
\v 34 Yesu lewexe wou xel, “Inye xel se byex eivek xam xe petieing, 
\q1 ‘A neimbei xam on anutuyeiw?’ \rq Qapiya Lalo 82:6\rq* 
\p  
\v 35 Wangwei moxo na neimbei xel anutu yon inyon wou eti yeiw wei qou qayeeng wei Anutu yo om xoulek on tyek se pakei na ba nge.  
\v 36 Ekom nambei nya xam ghe neimbei a lukyak lek Anutu, en ingwei a neimbei ay Anutu Neu yo? Inye a tambiy tiwei Anutu beyal me wong e lam lek tembuing o.  
\v 37 Wangwei a se bong xuk wei Mang mi wong o ond xam seng bongis ay.  
\v 38 Ekom wangwei a bong e xe xuk, ek xam seng bongis ay, ond xam ghe bongis xuk wei ay yo me ghe boulek bei Mang toundei eivek a laleing, de a toundei eivek Mang lalei.”  
\v 39 Xel di wong me yei en xel embei zeimaxoun e no, ekom moxo ghanaw xel me la. 
\p  
\v 40 Woyom Yesu lox me la sek memiing Yorodan me la beyeeng wei Yoan lipek xel lek bouk myaxeeng o. Moxo toundei inyon  
\v 41 me xomaxoneing ngenong lam wou e. Xel neil embei, “Yoan se wong dee wei lulvako yo ti, qe lul dalus wei Yoan neil lek tambiy tine eno zonghek.”  
\v 42 De eivek beyeeng tiyon eno xel ngenongakes wongis Yesu. 
\c 11  
\s1 Meyeing wei Laserus o 
\p  
\v 1 Ekom inyei tambiy ti lei Laserus eno vanei wong. Moxo nanghei Betani, beyeeng wei Maria luw li vex Marata yo.  
\v 2 Maria tiyon, takwei eno taw wel xeimangou lek Tambiy Ngandoung me vu e vaxa en luvelus, eno li moux Laserus vanei wong me e di yeip.  
\v 3 Om li vex aluw wong qayeeng la wou Yesu bei, “Tambiy Ngandoung, moux tiwei wa laleim vind eno vanei wong.” 
\p  
\v 4 Ka ingwei Yesu ngo inyon eno moxo neil embei, “Vanei yon se en ingwei xomaxoneing embei mey o. Ma, inyon embei talex Anutu xe nikanzek wou moux alis vex en xel bong e lei na, en kandek xel bong Anutu Neu Moux na qou lei ngandoung is.”  
\v 5 Yesu lalei vind Marata me li vex me Laserus.  
\v 6 Ekom gyeik ingwei moxo ngo bei Laserus vanei wong, eno toundei inyon teyei lek bouk yuw is no. 
\p  
\v 7 Woyom moxo neil wou e xe xel betiyeing bei, “Xey ambei nox me na Yudia.” 
\p  
\v 8 Xel neil embei, “Putoung se ghei denlek ingwei Yudayeiw embei banex wang en qakous o ti, ekom wa being nox me na inyei no?” 
\p  
\v 9 Yesu lewexe, “Beip inye se seivma xoumeeng yuw lek bendiyeing ti? Tambiy tiwei mi velewexe bendiyeing eno se mi beng en mi yei tembuing xe xeiyaing.  
\v 10 Ekom gyeik ingwei e velewexe eivek boukeing eno tyek na beng en xeiyaing ma veil e.” 
\p  
\v 11 E neil tine dekakom moxo neil wou xel, “Xe xe gweleeng Laserus yeip, ekom ambei na inyei en nana piyexe e.” 
\p  
\v 12 E xe xel betiyeing neil elox bei, “Tambiy Ngandoung, wangwei emdi gyeip on tyek bo nimzalek.”  
\v 13 Yesu neil en ingwei e xe meyeing o, ekom e xe xel betiyeing embeik nge Laserus di yeip. 
\p  
\v 14 Om moxo neilteyei wou xel bei, “Laserus mey,  
\v 15 de en xam eno a wo xeinglala ngandoung en a se toundei inyei, om tyek xam ghe bongis. Ekom xey ambei na wou e.” 
\p  
\v 16 Woyom Tomas (wei xel mi neil Didimas) eno neil wou xel betiyeing valu bei, “Wong xey dalus a la, en nana mey is e yo.” 
\s1 Yesu qes wei qandieing lek me mapieing o 
\p  
\v 17 Gyeik Yesu la eivek Betani eno ngo bei Laserus mey woy me xel ev eivek leiveeng meyeing de bouk vey la veil.  
\v 18 Betani toundei paviy Yerusalem nambei kilomita yayal,  
\v 19 de xel Yudayeiw ngenong lam toundei is Marata luw Maria me byexaxoun luw en ingwei li moux mey o.  
\v 20 Marata ngo bei Yesu lam, eno la myayaing en embei na pelong e, dom Maria toundei eivek xomek. 
\p  
\v 21 Marata neil wou Yesu bei, “Tambiy Ngandoung, wangwei wa toumendei inye nei on tyek a ling se mey.  
\v 22 Ekom gweimbeeng a woulek bei Anutu tyek bong vati wei wambei teling wou e yo.” 
\p  
\v 23 Yesu neil wou vexo bei, “Wa lim moux tyek qandi lek no.” 
\p  
\v 24 Marata lewexe bei, “A woulek bei moxo tyek qandi lek no eivek bouk loxyus wei xel embei qandi lek o.” 
\p  
\v 25 Yesu neil wou vexo bei, “A maxow qandieing lek me mapieing qes. Xelti embei bongis ay eno tyek na toumendei mapieing gyeik e mey o,  
\v 26 de xel eti yeiw wei toundei mapieing me wongis ay eno tyek se teyei bei mey. Beip wang wongis tine?” 
\p  
\v 27 Marata neil wou Yesu bei, “Ee, Tambiy Ngandoung, a wongis bei wa Kilisi, Anutu Neu Moux, tambiy tiwei embei nam lek tembuing o.” 
\p  
\v 28 Deka Marata neil tine, eno lox me la taxe li Maria la nenyawes. De ngoung wou e, “Putoung lam toundei inye me di teling en wang.”  
\v 29 Maria ngo tine, eno vexo qandi lek daing me la wou Yesu.  
\v 30 Yesu seng ghei la eivek beyeeng, qe nanghei toundei beyeeng wei Marata la pelong e yo.  
\v 31 Xel Yudayeiw wei toundei is Maria eivek xomek me ghanduxoun e, eno yei ingwei vexo qandi lek daing me la myayaing om xel betiy e, xel embeik nge embei na bo talot anghei ingwei leiveeng meyeing nei. 
\p  
\v 32 Maria la tyip beyeeng wei Yesu toundei yo me yei e, eno vexo ev vaxakatu eivek wou moxo vaxa me neil, “Tambiy Ngandoung, wangwei wa toumendei inye nei on tyek a ling moux se mey.” 
\p  
\v 33 Yesu yei ingwei vexo eng, me Yudayeiw wei lam is e eno di eng is, om moxo lalei pyaxow me embei deeng.  
\v 34 Moxo teling bei, “Xam ghe liw e nanghei inya?” 
\p Xel neil elox bei, “Tambiy Ngandoung, lam me wei.” 
\p  
\v 35 Yesu eng. 
\p  
\v 36 Woyom Yudayeiw neil embei, “Xam wei ingwei moxo lalei mi vind e mouyo!” 
\p  
\v 37 Ekom xel valu neil embei, “Tambiy tine mi wong xel wei mentekeing eno mi yeila, ekom nambei nya se teyei bei devind tambiy tine veil meyeing?” 
\s1 Yesu piyexe Laserus veil meyeing 
\p  
\v 38 Yesu lalei pyaxow no me la ingwei leiveeng meyeing nei. Inyei eeng wei xel kwelexe eivek qakous me lax mya zeyi yo.  
\v 39 Moxo neil embei, “Xam wo qakous veil.” 
\p Marata wei li moux mey eno neil embei, “Ekom Tambiy Ngandoung, tyek bo niliy, en yeip inyon bouk vey la veil o.” 
\p  
\v 40 Woyom Yesu neil embei, “Beip a se neil wou wang bei wangwei wang bongis, on tyek wang gwei Anutu xe nikanzek ngandoung?” 
\p  
\v 41 Om xel qepei qakous veil. Woyom Yesu veilma lek me neil embei, “Mang, a wong dange wou wang en wang mi ngo ay.  
\v 42 A woulek bei taxombouk eno wang mi ngo ay, ekom a neil inye en nimza wei xomaxoneing wei toungale inye, bei xel bongis bei wang wong a lam.” 
\p  
\v 43 Ka Yesu neil tine woy, eno taxe xoulekeing bei, “Laserus, lam myayaing!”  
\v 44 Moux wei mey eno lam myayaing, xel beliv e mema luw me vaxa luw en qaeing de beliv qaeing vivekwou e ma. 
\p Yesu neil wou xel “Xam tul qaeing wei leiveeng meyeing eno veil de wong e la.” 
\s1 Xel tup qayeeng en xel embei nyeis Yesu na mey 
\p  
\v 45 Nambei nyon om Yudayeiw ngenong wei lam toundei is Maria, eno yei vati wei Yesu wong, om xel wongis e.  
\v 46 Ekom xel wei xel eno valu la neil wou xel Parisi en vati wei Yesu wong o.  
\v 47 Woyom xel lumuki leitata yo is Parisiyeiw taxe qekueing ama wei kanzol o. Xel teling bei, “Tyek xey a bong ambei nya? Tambiy tine wong dee wei lulvako yo ngenong.  
\v 48 Wangwei xey a bong emdi bong ambei nyon, on tyek xel dalus bongis e. De woyom tyek xel Rom nam lelolexe xe xe xomek vambuing de na qou xomaxoneing wei tembuing ne is.” 
\p  
\v 49 Woyom xel wei xel on ti, e lei Kaiapas, moxo wo lumuki lukanzek lek vakovek qes tiyon, eno luk wou xel bei, “Xam lumimpeyei se woulek lulti!  
\v 50 Xam seng woulek bei inye nimza wou xam en ingwei tambiy ti e mey en xomaxoneing dalus enok xel dalus wei tembuing tine eno na mey.” 
\p  
\v 51 Moxo se neil inyon nangya kwa, qe wo lumuki lukanzek lek vakovek qes tiyon om neil qayeeng poropet lek ingwei Yesu tyek na mey en xel wei Yudayeiw o,  
\v 52 De se en Yudayeiw venaxow qe en Anutu neuyeiw wei toundei lala yo en embei qeku xel dalus lekti me xel bo tixemou.  
\v 53 Om gyeik bouk kayon me e di la eno xel di luklek sakwaing wei xel embei nyeis Yesu e mey yo. 
\p  
\v 54 Nambei nyon om Yesu se lox me la ghavineeng yanyateiv eivek xel Yudayeiw senghoing. Moxo la veil inyon me la beyeeng wei di yeip paviy tembuing bandaing o, la beyeeng wei xel mi neil Epraim nei, me moxo is e xe xel betiyeing la mindei inyon. 
\p  
\v 55 Bouk la paviy Yudayeiw xe Pasova, om xel ngenong wei tembuing danghei danghei nei lek me la Yerusalem en embei na bo xow bo vako natax en Pasova.  
\v 56 Xel di yimexe Yesu, deka xel toukale eivek tete lalei wei xomek vambuing eno xel di teling wouma, “Xam ghe wou naleimim neing bei moxo tyek nam gyei bouk dalus wei Pasova ne?”  
\v 57 Ekom xel lumuki leitata me Parisiyeiw neil wou moux alis vex bei wangwei xelti boulek ingwei Yesu toundei yo, ond e neil wou xel en xel na zeimaxoun e. 
\c 12  
\s1 Maria taw wel lek Yesu nanghei Betani 
\p  
\v 1 Bouk limti nanghei di yeip zeyi Pasova, om Yesu la toundei Betani wei Laserus mindei lek o, inyon tambiy tiwei Yesu piyexe e qandi lek veil meyeing o.  
\v 2 Xel wo xeindlala en Yesu me wo mata ti wou e. Marata di duw yaeing, de Laserus toundei senghoing is xel wei di ya lek lelek is e yo.  
\v 3 Woyom Maria qou wel xeimangou wei malew ngandoung en o veweeng me taw lek Yesu vaxa de vu e vaxa nangya venaxow luvelus. Me xomek pup en wel on xeimangou. 
\p  
\v 4 Ekom e xe betiyeing ti, Yudas Iskariot, wei tyek na neil e teyei me na toung e na eivek xel ba memend loxyus o, eno neil embei,  
\v 5 “Nambei nya wel xeimangou ne xey se wo vateivek lek me na qou malew selewa vaxak yal lek en na bo wou xel kanyo?”  
\v 6 Tambiy on se neil inyon en embei devind xel kanyo, qe nambei moxon panaxana, moxo mi yeiteyei qoupek malew wei xel o, om mi panax malew wei xel mi toung eivek o. 
\p  
\v 7 Yesu neil elox bei, “Wong vex on venaxow toundei, inye wo bombek bei zeimaxoun wel xeimangou yon bei menyex wou a neing en bouk wei eveing o.  
\v 8 Xel kanyo tyek na mi mendei eivek xam senghoing taxombouk, ekom tyek a se mendei is xam taxombouk.” 
\p  
\v 9 Dekalekom xel qendu ngandoung wei Yudayeiw eno ngo bei Yesu toundei Betani om xel la, se en e maxow qe xel embei na gyei Laserus tambiy tiwei Yesu piyexe e veil meyeing o.  
\v 10 Om xel lumuki leitata di luklek inye en xel embei nyeis Laserus a mey is,  
\v 11 en nambei xel wounaleind en ingwei Yesu wong wou Laserus, om xel ngenong wei Yudayeiw eno di la wou Yesu me wongis e. 
\s1 Yesu la eivek Yerusalem nambei king 
\p  
\v 12 Bouk nge eno xel qendu ngandoung wei lam en Pasova eno ngo bei Yesu di lam Yerusalem.  
\v 13 Xel qou zangholeng mema me la myayaing en xel embei na pelong e, xel di taxe bei, 
\q1 “Hosana!” 
\q1 “Mata ena wou tambiy tiwei lam lek Tambiy Ngandoung lei yo!” \rq Qapiya Lalo 118:25-26\rq* 
\q1 “Mata ena wou king wei Israel xe yo!” 
\m  
\v 14 Yesu yei dongi lingheing ti me dei lek, nambei xel byex eivek xoulek o, 
\q1  
\v 15 “Sayon neu vex wa seng gwaleeng, 
\q2 wei, wa xe king di lam, 
\q2 Moxo dei lek dongi lingheing ti.” \rq Sakarias 9:6\rq* 
\p  
\v 16 Myaxeeng eno e xe xel betiyeing se woulek lulti beimambei ne dalus qes. Qe ka Anutu wo lei ngandoung wou Yesu, om xel woulek xoulek wei yeip eivek qapiya yo, me xel wou naleind en lulti beimambei wei xel wong woy wou e yo. 
\p  
\v 17 Nanghei inyei eno xel qendu ngandoung wei toundei is e gyeik ingwei moxo taxe Laserus nanghei leiveeng meyeing me e qandi lek me lam veil meyeing eno xel di tetulexe qayeeng on lala.  
\v 18 En qes tine is ambei nyon xomaxoneing ngenong la pelong e en xel ngo ingwei e wong dee wei lulvako yo.  
\v 19 Om xel Parisiyeiw di neil wouma bei, “Wei, xey se teyei bei bo lulti. Xam ghe wei kwa yon, xel dalusateiv wei tembuing sapa eno la betiwou e.” 
\s1 Yesu neil e xe meyeing teyei 
\p  
\v 20 Xel Grik valu lam toundei senghoing eivek moux alis vex wei lam tyip en embei nam bo lalo lek bouk ngandoung tine yo.  
\v 21 Xel lam wou Pilip, tambiy wei nanghei Betsaida eivek Galili yo. Xel neil embei, “Teiv, xa bei ghei Yesu.”  
\v 22 Pilip la neil wou Andrias, de Andrias aluw Pilip la neil wou Yesu. 
\p  
\v 23 Yesu neil elox wou luw, “Bouk la wou eivek en ingwei Xomaxoneing Neu Moux embei bo lei ngandoung o.  
\v 24 A neil wou xam zonghek, Wangwei wit vei se detei lek tembuing me na mey, on tyek na toumendei nambei vei tixemou. Ekom wangwei e mey, on tyek bo vei ngenong.  
\v 25 Tambiy ti embei lalei devind mapieing wei e yo on tyek na saing e xe mapieing, ek wangwei tambiy ti embei toung demi wou e xe mapieing lek tembuing tine on tyek na zeimaxoun e xe mapieing luta luta.  
\v 26 Xelti embei bong a xe xuk ond e mi betiwou ay, me beyeeng wei ambei mendei eno a xe xukxe tyek mendei is ay. De Mang tyek bo lei ngandoung wou tambiy tiwei embei bong a xe xuk o. 
\p  
\v 27 “Gweimbeeng a laleing wo maying, me tyek a neil ambei nya? ‘Mang, wa devind a lek seivma tine’? Ma, a se neil ambei nye. En lek qes tiyon om a lam lek seivma tine.  
\v 28 Mang, wang bo leim bo ngandoung!” Woyom vya ti lam anghei tyoung gheyapu nei bei, “A wong e wo ngandoung woy, me tyek a bong embo ngandoung no.” 
\p  
\v 29 Om xel qendu ngandoung wei toukale inyon ngo vya ti me neil embei dewek toung, de valu neil embei angela ti luk is e. 
\p  
\v 30 Yesu neil embei, “Vya tine embei devind xam, de se ay.  
\v 31 Gweimbeeng inye bouk wei Anutu embei bong qayeeng en tembuing tine, de tyek na tiy gyovaxa tiwei mi yeiteyei tembuing tine yo na.  
\v 32 Ekom Ay, eno wangwei xel a zeim a zekna veil tembuing, on tyek a puw moux alis vex dalus noum wou xow.”  
\v 33 Moxo neil tiyon en embei talex ingwei tyek na mey ambei nya yo. 
\p  
\v 34 Xel qendu ngandoung on neil embei, “Xa ngo eivek petieing bei Kilisi tyek na mi mendei luta luta, om nambei nya wang neimbei, ‘Xomaxoneing Neu Moux tyek xel a zeim e zekna’? Inyon ‘Xomaxoneing eti Neu Moux’?” 
\p  
\v 35 Woyom Yesu neil wou xel bei, “Tyek xeiyaing a toumendei is xam bouk sepika. Om xam a mi na eivek xeiyaing, enok mapetok nam sevun xam. Tambiy wei mi la eivek mapetok eno se mi woulek ingwei embei na yo.  
\v 36 Xam a mi bongis xeiyaing wei xam ghe qou yo. En kandek xam ghe bo xeiyaing neuyeiw.” Yesu luk woy, eno moxo la veil xel de la xupek en xel. 
\s1 Xel Yudayeiw valu wongis Yesu de valu se wongis 
\p  
\v 37 Yesu wong dee wei lulvako beimambei yon wou xel mend woy, ekom xel se wongis e.  
\v 38 Tiyon wo neing lek nambei qayeeng wei poropet Yesaya yo: 
\q1 “Tambiy ngandoung, eti wongis xa xe qayeeng 
\q2 me Tambiy Ngandoung mema\f + \fr 12:38 \ft Mema qes ambei nye Anutu xe nikanzek.\f* talex lulul tine lam yanyateiv wou eti?” \rq Yesaya 53:1\rq* 
\p  
\v 39 En qes tiyon om moux alis vex se teyei bei bongis, en nambei Yesaya byex eivek qayeeng nge bei: 
\q1  
\v 40 “Moxo wong xel mend tek 
\q2 Me wong xel laleind wo nikanzek, 
\q1 enok xel mend gyeina, 
\q2 o xel boulek eivek laleind, 
\q2 o xel pekwi me noum me a bong xel bo nimzalek.” \rq Yesaya 6:10\rq* 
\m  
\v 41 Yesaya neil tine en nambei moxo yei Yesu xe xeiyaing ngandoung om neil inyon en e. 
\p  
\v 42 Neing, xel gyovaxa ngenong wei Yudayeiw o wongis Yesu. Ekom nambei xel Parisi om xel se neil xel xe wongeingis teyei en xel yaleeng enok xel a tiy xel veil xomek qekueing ama.  
\v 43 En xel laleind mi vind ingwei moux alis vex mi sanghoxe xel ghanaw ingwei Anutu mi sanghoxe yo. 
\p  
\v 44 Woyom Yesu taxe bei, “Wangwei xelti embei bongis ay, ond moxo se wongis a maxow, qe wongis tambiy tiwei wong a lam o.  
\v 45 De moxo embei gyei ay, ond moxo yei tambiy tiwei wong a lam o.  
\v 46 A lam tembuing ne nambei xeiyaing, en kandek xel wei wongis ay eno tyek se mendei eivek mapetok. 
\p  
\v 47 “En nambei xelti embei ngo a xe qayeeng ekom se betiwou, ond tyek a se bong qayeeng en e. En a se lam en ambei bong qayeeng en moux alis vex wei tembuing o, qe ambei devind xel veil nilul.  
\v 48 Inyei tambiy wei mi ngo qayeeng o ti toundei en embei bong qayeeng en tiwei se ngo ay me se qou a xe qayeeng o, qayeeng wei a mi neil eno tyek bo qayeeng en e lek bouk loxyus.  
\v 49 En a se mi neil inyon nangya kwang, qe Mang tiwei wong a lam eno peti wou ay en vati wei ambei neil me kwa wei ambei neil o.  
\v 50 A woulek bei e xe petieing on mapieing luta luta. Om vati wei a mi neil eno mi la nambei ingwei Mang neil wou ay bei a neil o.” 
\c 13  
\s1 Yesu lipek e xe xel betiyeing vaxend 
\p  
\v 1 Inye bouk paviy mata wei Pasova yo. Yesu woulek bei bouk lam en ingwei embei na veil tembuing me na wou Ma yo. Moxo lalei vind emaxow xe xel wei toundei lek tembuing o, me e lam gweimbeeng ne eno moxo lalei vind xel ghanaw veil. 
\p  
\v 2 De soukeing wei xel di ya eno Sandang toung kwa eivek Yudas Iskariot, Simon neu woy, bei e toung Yesu na eivek xel ba memend.  
\v 3 Yesu woulek bei ma toung lulul dalus la eivek e xe nikanzek xeinghembi, me ingwei Anutu wong e lam me ingwei tyek nox me na wou Anutu yo,  
\v 4 om moxo qandi lek veil yaeing, me kwax e xe teimb ding veil, de vex vetivek ti vivekwou xeikatu.  
\v 5 Kalekom moxo taw memiing lek dipekta ti de mouk sekweyexe e xe xel betiyeing vaxend, me vu xel vaxend nangya vetivek wei vex evivekwou xeikatu yo. 
\p  
\v 6 Moxo lam wou Simon Petele, e tiwei neil wou bei, “Tambiy Ngandoung, inye wa being zipek a vaxang?” 
\p  
\v 7 Yesu neil elox bei, “Wa seng woulek vati wei a wong gweimbeeng ne, qe kalekom tyek wang boulek loxyus.” 
\p  
\v 8 Petele neil embei, “Ma, wa seng teyei bei sekweyexe a vaxang se teyei.” 
\p Yesu lewexe bei, “Wangwei a se sekweyexe wang, on a se xe wang.” 
\p  
\v 9 Woyom Simon Petele neil elox bei, “Tambiy Ngandoung, wangwei nambei nyon nei on wa se sekweyexe a vaxang venaxow qe a memang me a lung is ambei nyon!” 
\p  
\v 10 Yesu neil embei, “Tambiy wei lipek woy eno tyek zipek vaxa venaxow dom neing dalus wo vako. De xam ghe wo vako, ekom se xam on dalus.”  
\v 11 En Yesu woulek tambiy tiwei embei toung e na eivek xel ba memend o, omek ingwei neil embei xam dalus seng wo vako. 
\p  
\v 12 Ka moxo lipek xel vaxend ma, eno moxo byex e xe teimb ding lek de lox me la dei lek nimbeeng. 
\p Moxo teling wou xel, “Xam ghe woulek vati wei a wong wou xam ne?  
\v 13 Xam ghe mi taxe a ‘Putoung’ me ‘Tambiy Ngandoung,’ om inyon nimza, en inyei ay ambei nyon.  
\v 14 A ne xam xe Tambiy Ngandoung me Putoung, de a lipek xam vaxamim, om xam is ambei nyon xam a mi zipek ama vaxamim.  
\v 15 A talex kwa ne wou xam bei xam a mi bong ambei ingwei a wong wou xam ne.  
\v 16 A neil wou xam zonghek, xukxe ti se ghanaw e xe teiv, o nenyalesana se ghanaw tambiy wei wong e la yo.  
\v 17 Gweimbeeng xam ghe woulek lulti beimambei ne, om wangwei xam ghe bong lulti yon dalus on tyek xam a qou mata. 
\s1 Yesu neil e la tax en tambiy wei tyek na neil e teyei yo 
\p  
\v 18 “A se neil xam dalus. A woulek xam wei a beyal o. Ekom tine embo neing lek ambei ingwei di yeip eivek xoulek o. 
\q1 ‘Tambiy tiwei ya belet is ay eno tyek bo vaxaghelu zekna me bakei ay.’ \rq Qapiya Lalo 41:9\rq* 
\p  
\v 19 “A neil inye natax wou xam gweimbeeng dom inye se ghei qandi, en kandek gyeik ingwei embei qandi on xam ghe bongis bei A maxow Tambiy Tiyon.  
\v 20 A neil wou xam zonghek, xelti embei qou eti yeiw wei a wong e lak on qou ay, me xelti embei qou ay on qou tambiy tiwei wong a lam o.” 
\p  
\v 21 Ka ingwei moxo neil tine, eno Yesu lalei wo maying, me neil embei, “A neil wou xam zonghek, xam venaxow ti tyek na neil a teyei me na toung a na eivek xel ba memend.” 
\p  
\v 22 Moxo xe xel betiyeing di yei ma kanzek en nambei xel se woulek bei neil eti.  
\v 23 De Yesu xe betiyeing tiwei lalei mi vind e eno di yeip pepeeng lek zek paviy e.  
\v 24 Simon Petele bimexe lu me neil wou betiyeing tiyon bei, “Teling wou e bei moxo neil eti.” 
\p  
\v 25 Om betiyeing tiyon li lu la paviy Yesu bambou de teling bei, “Tambiy Ngandoung, inyon eti?” 
\p  
\v 26 Yesu lewexe bei, “Tambiy tiwei ambei toung belet danghei ti eivek louk me na bong wou eno tiyon inyon.” Woyom toung belet danghei ti eivek louk me wong wou Yudas Iskariot Simon neu.  
\v 27 Ka Yudas ya woy, Sandang la eivek e. 
\p De Yesu neil wou e, “Lul vati wei wa being bong, eno wang bong daing.”  
\v 28 Ekom xel wei toundei me ya eno ti se woulek bei nambei nya Yesu neil tiyon wou e.  
\v 29 En nambei Yudas mi yeiteyei qoupek wei malew o, om xel betiyeing valu embeik nge Yesu neil wou e bei e na bou lulul en mata wei bouk ngandoung, o bong lulul wou xel kanyo.  
\v 30 Lutika eno Yudas ya belet wei Yesu wong wou e yo, de moxo la myayaing. De inye bouk. 
\s1 Yesu neil embei tyek Petele dax e vun 
\p  
\v 31 Yudas la veil woy, eno Yesu neil embei, “Gweimbeeng Xomaxoneing Neu Moux tyek bo lei ngandoung me Anutu tyek na qou lei ngandoung en Neu.  
\v 32 Wangwei Anutu na qou lei ngandoung en e, ond Anutu tyek bong lei ngandoung wou emaxow Neu Moux, me tyek bo lei ngandoung wou moxo lutika. 
\p  
\v 33 “A neungyeiw, tyek a toumendei is xam enden nayaka. De tyek xam ghe gwimexe ay, nambei ingwei a neil wou xel Yudayeiw o, om a neil wou xam gweimbeeng: Ingwei ambei na nei eno tyek xam seng nam. 
\p  
\v 34 “Ambei bong petieing vako wou xam: Xam laleimim e mi devind xel nge. Nambei ingwei a laleing vind xam o, om xam laleimim emi devind xel nge.  
\v 35 Nangya tine eno wangwei xam laleimim devind xel nge ond tyek xomaxoneing dalus boulek bei xam on a xe betiyeing.” 
\p  
\v 36 Simon Petele teling wou bei, “Tambiy Ngandoung, wa being na nya?” 
\p Yesu neil elox bei, “Ingwei ambei na nei eno tyek wa se betiwou gweimbeeng, qe tyek wa betiwou loxyus.” 
\p  
\v 37 Petele teling, “Tambiy Ngandoung, nambei nya tyek a se betiwou wang gweimbeeng? Tyek a saing a xe mapieing en wang.” 
\p  
\v 38 Woyom Yesu lewexe bei, “Neing, tyek wang teyei bei saing wa xe mapieing en ay? A neil wou wang zonghek, gyeik qouklex se ghei sesa vya, eno tyek wang dax a vun luyal!” 
\c 14  
\s1 Yesu byexaxoun e xe xel betiyeing 
\p  
\v 1 Yesu neil embei, “Xam laleimim se bo maying. Xam ghe bongis Anutu, me xam ghe bongis ay is ambei nyon.  
\v 2 Eivek Mang xe xomek nei eno lalei ngenong, wangwei se nambei nyon nei, on tyek a se neil wou xam. Om ambei na inyei me na menyex beyeeng wou xam.  
\v 3 Me wangwei a na menyex wou xam bamim nei, on tyek a noum a qou xam me nana is xow, me beyeeng wei ambei mendei eno tyek xam ghe na mendei is ay.  
\v 4 Xam ghe woulek sakwaing wei la beyeeng tiwei ambei na yo.” 
\s1 Yesu e sakwaing wei la wou Ma yo 
\p  
\v 5 Tomas neil wou e, “Tambiy Ngandoung, xa se woulek ingwei wa being na yo, om nambei nya tyek xa boulek sakwaing?” 
\p  
\v 6 Yesu neil embei, “A maxow sakwaing me zonghek me mapieing qes. Xelti tyek se nam wou Mang eivek sakwaing nge qe a maxow.  
\v 7 Wangwei xam ghe boulek a boy nei, on tyek xam ghe boulek Mang is. Gweimbeeng ne me e mi na eno xam ghe woulek moxo me ghe wei e.” 
\p  
\v 8 Pilip neil embei, “Tambiy Ngandoung, talex Mam wou xa, en e teyei lek xa laleimi yo.” 
\p  
\v 9 Yesu neil embei: “Pilip, inye wa seng ghei woulek ay? De a mindei eivek xam senghoing me enden eno? Xelti embei gyei ay eno yei Mang. Nambei nya wang neimbei, ‘Talex Mang wou xa’?  
\v 10 Beip wa seng wongis bei a toundei eivek Mang, de Mang toundei eivek ay? Qayeeng wei a neil wou xam eno inye se a maxow. Qe inye Mang toundei eivek Ay, me di wong e xe xuk.  
\v 11 Xam ghe bongis ay gyeik ingwei a neimbei a toundei eivek Mang de Mang toundei eivek ay, o xam ghe bongis xuk dalus wei a mi wong o.  
\v 12 A neil wou xam zonghek, xelti embei bongis ay on tyek bong vati wei a di wong ne, moxo tyek bong lul ngandoung beimambei ne ghanaw ingwei a wong ne, en nambei ambei na wou Mang.  
\v 13 De tyek a bong vatiyeiw wei xam ghe teling en eivek a leing o, en kandek Neu Moux bo lei ngandoung wou Ma.  
\v 14 Xam a mi teling wou ay en lul vatiyeiw eivek a leing, de tyek a bong. 
\s1 Yesu neil zonghek bei tyek bong Laweeng Vambuing nam 
\p  
\v 15 “Wangwei xam laleimim devind ay, on tyek xam betiwou petieing wei a neil wou xam o.  
\v 16 De tyek a teling wou Mang, me e bong Vineing nge wou xam en e mi mendei is xam takwei takwei.  
\v 17 Vineing tiyon Laweeng wei zonghek o. Moux alis vex wei tembuing ne se qou e, en nambei xel se yei moxo, o xel se woulek e. Ekom xam ghe woulek e, en nambei moxo toundei is xam me tyek na toumendei eivek xam.  
\v 18 Tyek a se saing xam nambei yak pemboung. Tyek a mi nam wou xam.  
\v 19 Bouk sepika moux alis vex wei tembuing ne tyek se gyei a no, qe tyek xam ghe gwei ay. En nambei a toundei mapieing, de xam is ambei nyon tyek xam a toumendei mapieing.  
\v 20 Lek bouk tiyon eno tyek xam ghe boulek bei a toundei eivek Mang de xam ghe toundei eivek ay, de a toundei eivek xam.  
\v 21 Xelti embei qou a xe petieing me betiwou, ond tiyon lalei vind ay. Xelti embei lalei devind ay ond tyek Mang lalei devind e, me ay is ambei nyon tyek a laleing devind e me talex xow wou e.” 
\p  
\v 22 Woyom Yudas (se Yudas Iskariot) neil embei, “Ekom Tambiy Ngandoung, nambei nya wambei talex xow wou xa maxow de se wou moux alis vex wei tembuing sapa yo?” 
\p  
\v 23 Yesu neil elox bei, “Wangwei xelti lalei devind ay, ond tyek betiwou a xe teyoxeing. De Mang tyek lalei devind e, me tyek uw a nam wou moxo me na nam a mi mendei is e.  
\v 24 Tambiy ti lalei se mi vind ay eno tyek se betiwou a xe teyoxeing. Qayeeng beimambei wei xam ghe ngo ne eno inyon se a maxow xe, qe xel xouing on Mang tiwei wong a lam eno xe. 
\p  
\v 25 “A neil wou xam en lulul tine dalus gyeik a toundei is xam o.  
\v 26 Ekom Vineing, Laweeng Vambuing, wei Mang tyek bong e nam eivek a leing, eno tyek teyoxe xam en lul dalus me beil xam lumim lek en lulul sapa wei a neil wou xam woy yo.  
\v 27 Lalei vevopeing a wong e toundei is xam, a xe lalei vevopeing a wong wou xam. A se wong wou xam nambei xel wei tembuing sapa ne mi wong o. Om xam laleimim se bo maying me xam seng gwaleeng. 
\p  
\v 28 “Xam ghe ngo ingwei a neil o woy, ‘Ambei na de na noumenam wou xam.’ Wangwei xam laleimim devind ay, ond tyek xam ghe bo xeilala en ingwei ambei na wou Mang o, en Mang lei ngandoung eno ngandoung ghanaw ay.  
\v 29 A neil tiyon wou xam atax de se ghei qandi, en kandek gyeik ingwei embei qandi, on tyek xam ghe bongis.  
\v 30 Tyek a se puw qayeeng is xam, en gyovaxa wei mi yeiteyei tembuing ne eno lam. Moxo nikanzek se teyei bei bo lulti wou ay,  
\v 31 ekom ambei xomaxoneing wei tembuing sapa eno boulek bei a laleing vind Mang me na mi wong nambei kawei Mang peti bei a bong o. 
\p “Xam qandi lek, en xey a na yo.” 
\c 15  
\s1 Wain me mema mema 
\p  
\v 1 Yesu neil embei, “A maxow yis wain zonghek de Mang on xuk wain ma.  
\v 2 Moxo pyaw mema dalus wei byexlek ay eno veil en xel se vuk neing lek, de mema mema wei mi vuk eno Mang qateiv veil en kandek embuk neing ngenong lek.  
\v 3 Xam ghe wo vako woy en qayeeng wei a mi neil wou xam o.  
\v 4 Xam a mi mendei eivek ay, de tyek a mi mendei eivek xam. Mema ti tyek se buk neing lek nangya emaxow, qe e mendei eivek wain bole. Xam is tyek xam seng buk neing lek qe ka xam mendei eivek a bole. 
\p  
\v 5 “A maxow wain qes, de xam mema mema. Wangwei tambiy ti embei mendei eivek ay me a mendei eivek e, ond tyek buk neing ngenong, ek wambei mendei beyaleing veil ay on tyek wa seng bo lulti.  
\v 6 Xelti embei se mendei eivek ay, ond inyon nambei mema wei xel nex ela me e mupek o, om mema nambei nyon tyek xel qekuwou me banex ena me besei lek nenyex.  
\v 7 Wangwei xam mendei eivek ay me a xe qayeeng mendei eivek xam, ond xam teling vatiyeiw en woueing nalei wei xam o, on tyek bong wou xam.  
\v 8 Xam ghe buk neing ngenong lek en e talex bei xam on a xe betiyeing, de inyon embong lei ngandoung wou Mang. 
\p  
\v 9 “Nambei ingwei Mang lalei vind ay, om a laleing vind xam. Gweimbeeng xam a mi mendei eivek a xe lalei vineing.  
\v 10 Wangwei xam betiwou a xe petieing ond tyek xam mendei eivek a xe lalei vineing, nambei ingwei a betiwou Mang xe petieing me na toundei eivek e xe lalei vineing o.  
\v 11 A neil wou xam en tine en kandek a xe xeilala e mi mendei eivek xam de xeilala tiyon e pup xam laleimim lek.  
\v 12 A xe petieing eno nambei nye: Xam titi laleimim e mi devind xel nge nambei ingwei a laleing vind xam o.  
\v 13 Lalei vineing ngandoung wei xelti eno nambei nye, tambiy ti e saing e xe mapieing en e xe gweleeng.  
\v 14 Xam on a xe gweleeng wangwei xam betiwou petieing wei a neil wou xam o.  
\v 15 Tyek a se nox me na taxe xukxe lek xam no, en nambei xukxe se woulek vati wei e xe teiv mi wong o, qe a taxe gweleeng lek xam, en lulul dalus wei a ngo wou Mang eno a neilteyei wou xam.  
\v 16 Xam seng beyal ay, qe a beyal xam bei xam ghe na me ghe buk neing lek, neing on tyek na mi mendei enden. Woyom Mang tyek bong vati wei xam ambei teling en eivek a leing eno wou xam.  
\v 17 Inye a xe petieing: Xam titi laleimim e mi devind ama. 
\s1 Xel wei tembuing o laleind tyek se devind xel betiyeing 
\p  
\v 18 “Wangwei moux alis vex wei tembuing ne bo lalei vanei wou xam ond xam ghe bou naleimim bei xel wong lalei vanei wou ay a tax.  
\v 19 Wangwei xam on ingwei tembuing ne yo, on tyek xel laleind devind xam nambei xel venaxow. Ekom xam se ingwei tembuing ne, en a beyal xam veil tembuing. En qes tiyon om moux alis vex wei tembuing ne di wo lalei vanei wou xam.  
\v 20 Xam ghe bou naleimim en qayeeng wei a neil wou xam o: ‘Xukxe ti se ghanaw e xe teiv.’ Wangwei xel bo nol wou ay, ond tyek xel bo nol wou xam is. Wangwei xel betiwou a xe teyoxeing ond tyek xel betiwou xam xe is.  
\v 21 Xel tyek bo nol wou xam en sakwaing ambei nyon en nambei a leing, en xel se woulek tambiy tiwei wong a lam o.  
\v 22 Wangwei a se nam me baluk wou xel nei ond sewokeing ma veil xel. Ekom gweimbeeng ne xel se teyei bei dax sewokeing wei xel eno vun.  
\v 23 Xelti embei bo lalei vanei wou ay ond wo lalei vanei wou Mang is.  
\v 24 Wangwei a se nam mendei eivek xel senghoing me na bong pok ngandoung wei xel nge se mi wong o ond tyek sewokeing ama veil xel. De xel yei lulvako beimambei ne woy, ekom xel laleind se vind ay me Mang is.  
\v 25 Ekom inye embei na teyei lek vati wei xel byex eivek petieing o: 
\q1 ‘Xel wo lalei vanei wou ay eno qes maeing.’ \rq Qapiya Lalo 35:19; 69:4\rq* 
\s1 Xuk wei Laweeng Vambuing o 
\p  
\v 26 “Gyeik tiwei embei devind en ghanduxoun xam eno nam ond tyek ambong e nak wou xam, inyei lam wou Mang, inyon Laweeng wei zonghek o wei mindei is Mang me lam eno tyek moxo na neil qayeeng en ay.  
\v 27 Me xam a neil qayeeng en ay is ambei nyon, en nambei xam ghe mindei is ay eivek myaxeeng selis. 
\c 16  
\p  
\v 1 “A neil inye wou xam woy en ambei xam se toung demimim wou ay.  
\v 2 Tyek xel a tiy xam veil xomek qekueing ama, deka bouk wei yo nam on tyek xel nyeis xam amey, de tyek xel bounaleind bei xel sei xound nimza wou Anutu.  
\v 3 Tyek xel bong kwa ti beimambei yon en xel se woulek Mang o ay.  
\v 4 A neil wou xam woy en tine, en kandek gyeik ingwei bouk on embei nam on tyek xam ghe bou naleimim bei a peti xam woy. A se neil ti beimambei ne wou xam myaxeeng en nambei a toundei is xam. 
\s1 Xuk wei Laweeng Vambuing o 
\p  
\v 5 “Ekom gweimbeeng ambei na wou tambiy tiwei wong a lam o, ekom xam ti seng teling ay bei, ‘Wa being na nya?’  
\v 6 Qe xam laleimim wo nimaying en nambei a neil ti beimambei ne woy wou xam.  
\v 7 Ekom a neil wou xam zonghek: Inye nimza wou xam en ingwei ambei na yo. Wangwei a se na, ond tyek Laweeng Vineing wei embei devind xam eno tyek se nam. Ekom wangwei a na, ond tyek a bong e nak wou xam.  
\v 8 Ka moxo embei nam, ond tyek bong moux alis vex wei tembuing o boulek sewokeing qes me kwa wei bombek eno qes me Anutu embei bong qayeeng eno qes:  
\v 9 Om sewokeing qes eno nambei nye, xomaxoneing se wongis ay.  
\v 10 Eivek kwa wei bombek eno nambei nye, ambei na wou Mang, de tyek xam seng nox mena gwei a no.  
\v 11 Me Anutu embei bong qayeeng eno qes ambei nye, gyovaxa tiwei mi yeiteyei tembuing eno nale lek qayeeng woy. 
\p  
\v 12 “A xe qayeeng ngenong wei ambei neil wou xam, ekom gweimbeeng xam seng teyei bei zeimaxoun.  
\v 13 Ekom gyeik e, Laweeng Zonghek nam, ond tyek beil xam lumim lek en qayeeng zonghek dalus. Moxo tyek se neil qayeeng nangya e maxow xe kwa, qe tyek na neil vati wei ngo yo teyei, me moxo tyek na neil lul wei mendi nam yus o wou xam.  
\v 14 Moxo tyek bong lei ngandoung wou ay, en nambei moxo tyek na qou lul wei a xe yo me na neilteyei wou xam.  
\v 15 Lulul dalus wei Mang xe eno inye a xe. En qes tiyon om ingwei a neimbei Laweeng tyek na qou lul wei a xe yo me na neilteyei wou xam.” 
\s1 Xel betiyeing xe lalei maying tyek pekwi xeilala 
\p  
\v 16 Yesu neil no bei, “Eivek bouk sepika eno tyek xam seng gwei a no, dekakom eivek bouk sepika eno tyek xam ghe gwei ay.” 
\p  
\v 17 Moxo xe xel betiyeing valu di neil wouma bei, “Inye neil qayeeng tine qes nambei nya, wei neil embei, ‘Eivek bouk sepika eno tyek xam seng gwei a no, dekakom eivek bouk sepika eno tyek xam ghe gwei ay.’ De moxo neil is ambei nye, ‘Qes bei ambei na wou Mang’?”  
\v 18 Xel di embek teling wouma bei, “Moxo neil ‘bouk sepika’ inye qes ambei nya? Xe se woulek vati wei e neil o.” 
\p  
\v 19 Yesu yei bei xel embei teling e en inyon, om moxo neil wou xel bei, “Xam ghe di teling ama en vati wei a neil o qes gyeik ingwei a neimbei, ‘Eivek bouk sepika eno tyek xam seng gwei a no, de woyom ka eivek bouk sepika eno tyek xam ghe gwei ay.’  
\v 20 A neil wou xam zonghek, tyek xam ghe deeng me ghe bo talot, de xomaxoneing wei tembuing sapa eno tyek bo xeindlala, de xam laleimim tyek bo maying, ekom lalei maying wei xam eno tyek pekwi me bo xeilala.  
\v 21 Vex ti embei bou neu eno axe vanei en e ning bouk lam, ekom gyeik ingwei vexo neu umbek eno wo xeilala de nalei ma vanei yon en nambei neu umbek woy lek tembuing.  
\v 22 Om xam is: Gweimbeeng xam laleimim tyek bo maying, ekom tyek anghei xam no de tyek xam ghe bo xeimimlala, de xelti tyek se zeim xam xe xeilala veil.  
\v 23 De eivek bouk tiyon eno tyek xam se teling ay en lulti. A neil wou xam zonghek, Mang tyek bong vatiyeiw wei xam ghe teling en a leing eno wou xam.  
\v 24 Takwei eno xam seng teling lulul ti en a leing. Xam teling ond tyek xam a qou, de tyek xam xe xeilala na pup xam lek. 
\p  
\v 25 “A mi neil qayeeng wou xam eivek pakeing, de gyeik ingwei bouk ti tyek nam eno tyek a se nox a neil vya nambei nyon no qe tyek a neil e gyeip yaing wou xam en Mang.  
\v 26 Eivek bouk tiyon eno tyek xam teling en a leing. A se neimbei tyek a teling wou Mang en xam.  
\v 27 Ma. Mang venaxow lalei vind xam en nambei xam laleimim vind a woy me ghe wongis bei a lam anghei ingwei Anutu toundei nei.  
\v 28 A lam anghei ingwei Mang toundei nei me na lam tembuing, de gweimbeeng tyek a na veil tembuing me na nox me na wou Mang.” 
\p  
\v 29 Woyom Yesu xe xel betiyeing neil embei, “Gweimbeeng wang neil e yeip yaing dom wa seng neil qayeeng pakeing.  
\v 30 Xa xei bei wang woulek lulul dalusateiv me wa seng wou naleim bei xelti teling wou wang. Tine wong xa wongis bei wang lam anghei ingwei Anutu mindei nei.” 
\p  
\v 31 Yesu neil embei, “Gweimbeeng xam ghe wongis?”  
\v 32 Ekom bouk di lam paviy, me lam tyip paviy, gyeik ingwei xel embei tiy xam davuna bamim titi yo. Tyek xam ghe na veil ay me a toumendei venaxow, ekom a maxow se toundei, en Mang toundei is ay. 
\p  
\v 33 “A neil wou xam woy en lulul ti beimambei ne, en kandek eivek ay eno tyek xam a qou lalei vevopeing. De eivek tembuing ne eno tyek xam a qou nimaying. Ekom xam laleimim se bo maying! En a xoklek nikanzek wei tembuing ne yo.” 
\c 17  
\s1 Yesu zeimema bei Ma bong e qou lei ngandoung 
\p  
\v 1 Ka Yesu neil tiyon woy, eno yeila tyoung gheyapu me zeimema: 
\pm “Mang, seivma la wou eivek woy. Wang bong lei ngandoung wou Neum Moux, en kandek Neum Moux bo lei ngandoung wou wang.  
\v 2 En wang wong lei wei nikanzek eno wou moxo woy ghanaw xomaxoneing sapa wei e teyei bei bong mapieing luta luta wou xel wei wang wo wou e woy yo.  
\v 3 Inye deing mapieing wei luta luta yo: wei xel woulek wang o, wamaxow tixemou Anutu zonghek, me Yesu Kilisi wei wang wong e lam o.  
\v 4 A wong wa leim wo ngandoung lek tembuing, de na wong xuk wei wang wong wou ay bei a bong eno ma.  
\v 5 De gweimbeeng, Mang wang bong lei ngandoung wou ay eivek wa mamghalus, lei ngandoung tiwei a qou takwei gyeik a toundei is wang de tembuing se ghei qandi yo. 
\s1 Yesu zeimema en e xe xel betiyeing 
\pm  
\v 6 “A neil wa leim teyei wou xel wei wang wong wou ay veil tembuing ne yo. Xel ne wa xe, wang wong xel wou ay me xel mi betiwou wa xe qayeeng.  
\v 7 Gweimbeeng xel woulek bei lulul sapa wei wang wong wou a ne lam wou wang.  
\v 8 En a wong qayeeng dalus wei wang wong wou ay eno wou xel me xel qou dalus. De xel woulek neing ayang bei a lam anghei ingwei wang mindei yon, me xel wongis bei wang wong a lam.  
\v 9 A zeimemang en xel. A se zeimemang en xomaxoneing wei tembuing sapa yo, qe xel wei wang wong wou ay yo, en xel on wa xe.  
\v 10 Xel dalus wei a xe eno inyon wa xe, de xel dalus wei wa xe eno inyon a xe. Me lei wei ngandoung eno lam wou ay eivek xel.  
\v 11 Tyek a se toumendei enden lek tembuing, qe tyek xel a toumendei lek tembuing, de a di lam wou wang. Mang vambuing, wa mi bale zeyi xel nangya wa leim, lei tiyon wang wong wou ay, en kandek xel bo tixemou nambei uw a wo tixemou yo.  
\v 12 Bouk wei a mindei is xel, eno a mi nale zeyi xel en wa leim me na mi xeiteyei xel en lei tiwei wang wong wou ay yo. De xelti se lati qe tixemou wei tyek na qou nilul o, en kandek qayeeng wei di yeip eivek qapiya eno bo neing lek. 
\pm  
\v 13 “A di lam wou wang gweimbeeng, ekom a neil ti beimambei ne gyeik a toundei lek tembuing ne, en kandek xel a qou a xe xeilala me e pup xel laleind lek.  
\v 14 A wong wa xe qayeeng wou xel de moux alis vex wei tembuing ne laleind wo nol wou xel, en xel ne eno se nanghei tembuing ne en nambei a se nanghei tembuing.  
\v 15 A xe zeimeing mema ne se en ingwei wambei zeim xel veil tembuing ne qe wa mi bale zeyi xel en tambiy tiwei nilul o.  
\v 16 Xel ne se nanghei tembuing, nambei a ne se nanghei tembuing.  
\v 17 Wang bong xel on bo vambuing beyaleing nangya wa xe qayeeng zonghek, en wa xe qayeeng on zonghek.  
\v 18 Nambei wang wong a lam lek tembuing, om a wong xel la eivek tembuing.  
\v 19 En a beyal venaxow wo vambuing en xel, en kandek xel bo vambuing zonghek. 
\s1 Yesu zeimema en xel wongeingis dalus 
\pm  
\v 20 “A xe zeimeing mema ne se en xel venaxow. Qe a zeimemang is ambei nyon en xel wei tyek na ngo xel xe qayeeng me bongis ay yo,  
\v 21 Mang, a bei xel bo tixemou, nambei wang mindei eivek ay de a mindei eivek wang o. Me xel mendei eivek uw en kandek moux alis vex wei tembuing ne bongis bei wang wong a lam.  
\v 22 A wong lei ngandoung tiwei wang wong wou ay eno wou xel en xel a mi mendei tixemou nambei uw a mindei tixemou yo.  
\v 23 A toundei eivek xel de wang toundei eivek ay. De ambei xel mendei tixemou en xel wei tembuing ne boulek bei wang wong a lam, de wa laleim devind xel nambei wa laleim vind ay yo. 
\pm  
\v 24 “Mang, ambei moux alis vex wei wang wong wou a ne eno na mendei lek beyeeng wei ambei mendei yo, me gyei a xe xeiyaing ngandoung me lei ngandoung wei wang wong wou ay yo, en nambei wa laleim vind ay takwei wei tembuing anghei ma yo. 
\pm  
\v 25 “Mang wei bombek o, xomaxoneing wei tembuing ne se woulek wang, qe a woulek wang, me xel woulek bei wang wong a lam.  
\v 26 A talex wang wou xel, en vati wei wa laleim vind o, me tyek a mi tetulexe wou xel. Woyom tyek xel a qou lalei vineing nambei ingwei wang wong wou ay yo, me tyek a maxow a mi mendei eivek xel.” 
\c 18  
\s1 Xel zeimaxoun Yesu 
\p  
\v 1 Ka Yesu zeimema woy, eno lis e xe xel betiyeing sek memiing Kidron me la. Nanghei loxalu eno xuk oliv ti toundei inyon, om Yesu lis e xe xel betiyeing la eivek. 
\p  
\v 2 Yudas tiwei embei neil Yesu teyei me na toung e na eivek xel ba memend eno woulek beyeeng tiyon, en nambei Yesu lis e xe xel betiyeing mi qekuma lumama nanghei inyon.  
\v 3 Om Yudas lam eivek xuk oliv on me qou xel vevek qendu ti me xel belimbo wei xel lumuki leitata me xel Parisi wong eno me lam, xel zeim lam me zounghexeing me lulul wei vevek o. 
\p  
\v 4 Yesu woulek lul dalus wei embei qandi wou e yo, om moxo la paviy me teling xel, “Xam ghe di wimexe eti?” 
\p  
\v 5 Xel neil elox bei, “Yesu wei Nasaret o.” 
\p Yesu neil, “Ay inye.” De Yudas tiwei embei toung e eivek xel memend eno toukale inyon is xel.  
\v 6 Xel ngo ingwei Yesu neil embei, “Ay inye,” eno xel duxeind me lox dom beng me yeip lek tembuing. 
\p  
\v 7 Moxo lox me la teling xel no, “Xam ghe di wimexe eti?” 
\p De xel neil, “Yesu wei Nasaret o.” 
\p  
\v 8 Yesu lewexe, “A neil wou xam woy bei ay inye. Wangwei xam mendi gwimexe ay, yond xam ghe bong xel moux beimambei ne na.”  
\v 9 Tine wong ambei nye en kandek qayeeng wei e neil eno embo neing lek: “Xel wei wang wong wou ay eno ti tyek se nati.” 
\p  
\v 10 Woyom Simon Petele puw e xe ngeyeing vevek me qateiv xukxe wei lumuki lukanzek xe yo nenya payeiv tip. Xukxe tiyon lei Malkus. 
\p  
\v 11 Yesu luk nikanzek wou Petele, “Toung wa xe ngeyeing vevek lox eivek myabelis! Wambei tyek a se num eivek mayamya wei Mang wong wou ay yo?” 
\p  
\v 12 Woyom xel vevek qendu ti me xel beyeiv is xel belimbo wei Yudayeiw o zeimaxoun Yesu. Xel qo moxo nangya yis  
\v 13 me qou e me la tax wou Anas, Anas on Kaiapas yeing wei wo lumuki lukanzek lek vakovek qes tiyon o.  
\v 14 Kaiapas tiwei wo xoulek wou xel lei ngandoung wei Yuda yo, inye nimza bei moux tixemou e mey en xomaxoneing. 
\s1 Petele ax Yesu vun tiwei tax o 
\p  
\v 15 Simon Petele me betiyeing nge di betiy Yesu. En nambei lumuki lukanzek woulek betiyeing tine, om moxo la is Yesu eivek tete lalei wei lumuki lukanzek xe yo,  
\v 16 ekom Petele toundei myayaing paviy qapomb me axe. De betiyeing nge wei lumuki lukanzek woulek, eno loumelam neil wou vexawo wei di yeiteyei qapomb o me qou Petele me la lalei. 
\p  
\v 17 Vexawo wei mi yeiteyei qapomb eno teling wou Petele, “Wang ond se e xe betiyeing ti?” 
\p Moxo neil elox bei, “Ma, se ay.” 
\p  
\v 18 Inye wo nityuweing, om xel xukxe me beyeiv toukale vivekwou nenyex wei xel vev me di pavang xow o. Petele is ambei nyon toukale is xel me pavang xow. 
\s1 Lumuki lukanzek teling Yesu 
\p  
\v 19 Dekalekom lumuki lukanzek teling wou Yesu en e xe xel betiyeing me e xe qayeeng wei mi teyoxe yo. 
\p  
\v 20 Yesu neil elox bei, “A mi neil qayeeng yanyateiv wou xomaxoneing sapa, taxombouk eno a mi teyoxe xel eivek xomek qekueing ama, o eivek tete lalei wei xomek vambuing wei xel Yudayeiw mi qekuma yo. A se neil qayeeng ti xupekeing.  
\v 21 Wang teling ay enva? Wa teling xel wei mi ngo a xe qayeeng o. En neing ayang xel woulek vati wei a mi neil o.” 
\p  
\v 22 Yesu neil qayeeng tine woy eno beyeiv wei toukale paviy eno ti petapexe moxo ling. De neil embei, “Inye kwa wei wa being zewexe lek lumuki lukanzek eno nambei nyon?” 
\p  
\v 23 Yesu neil elox bei, “Wangwei a neil lulti sewok, ond wa neil sewokeing tiyon teyei. Ekom wangwei a neil zonghek, ond nambei nya wang petapexe ay?”  
\v 24 Woyom Anas wong Yesu la is yis wei xel tup e xoun o wou lumuki lukanzek Kaiapas. 
\s1 Petele ax Yesu vun luyal 
\p  
\v 25 Ka Simon Petele toukale me pavang xow, eno xel teling e, “Wangwei bei wa se e xe betiyeing ti?” 
\p Moxo axvun me neil embei, “Ma, se ay ti.” 
\p  
\v 26 Ekom Lumuki lukanzek xe xukxe ti, inye nipapu wei tambiy tiwei Petele qateiv e nenya tip o neil embei, “Beip a xei wang eivek xuk oliv is e?”  
\v 27 Petele lox me la axvun no, de lutika eno qouklex sesa vya. 
\s1 Xel qou Yesu me la wou Pailat 
\p  
\v 28 Woyom satiboukeing lul eno xel Yudayeiw qou Yesu me la veil xomek wei Kaiapas o me la xomek wei lei ngandoung wei seyap wei Rom o. Xel wou naleind bei tyek xel bo nilaxes wou Anutu ma, om tyek xel se gya mata wei Pasova yo. Om xel se la eivek xomek lalei wei lei ngandoung wei seyap o.  
\v 29 Om Pailat lam myayaing wou xel me teling, “Xam a being bong qayeeng lek tambiy tine en vati?” 
\p  
\v 30 Xel neil elox bei, “Wangwei e se bo kwa wei nilul o, ond tyek xa se qou e me na bong e nam wou wang.” 
\p  
\v 31 Pailat neil embei, “Xam venaxow a qou moxo me ghe na bong qayeeng en e nangya xam venaxow xe petieing.” 
\p Xel Yudayeiw neil elox, “Ekom xel peti xa bei xa se nyeis xelti mey.”  
\v 32 Tine wong ambei nyon en kandek qayeeng wei Yesu neil atax en e xe meyeing wei tyek na mey ambei nya eno bo neing lek. 
\p  
\v 33 Woyom Pailat lox me la eivek xomek lalei wei seyap o me taxe Yesu la wou e, de teling moxo bei, “Inye wa king wei Yudayeiw o?” 
\p  
\v 34 Yesu teling, “Inye wamaxow xe woueing nalei, o xel valu neil wou wang en ay?” 
\p  
\v 35 Pailat neil elox bei, “Inye a Yuda ti? Wa xe xel is xel lumuki leitata qou wang me lam wou ay. Wang wo vati?” 
\p  
\v 36 Yesu neil embei, “A xe tete lalei se nanghei tembuing ne. Wangwei nambei nyon on tyek a xe xel xukxe bo vevek zeyi ay, en kandek xel lei ngandoung wei Yuda eno se zeimaxoun ay. Ekom a xe tete lalei nanghei beyeeng bange.” 
\p  
\v 37 Pailat neil, “Inye wa king ti!” 
\p Yesu lewexe, “Inye wang neil bombek en ingwei wang neimbei a king ti yo. En qes tiyon om a umbek, me en tiyon eno a lam eivek tembuing en ambei nam a neil qayeeng zonghek teyei. Xel eti yeiw wei mi betiwou qayeeng zonghek eno mi ngo ay.” 
\p  
\v 38 Pailat teling, “Zonghek on vati?” De lox me la myayaing wou Yudayeiw no, wei di qekuma me neil embei, “A se xeiwou qayeeng qes ti eivek moxo bei xey a bo qayeeng en e.  
\v 39 Ekom inye xam venaxow xe kwa bei a mi bong xel wei toundei eivek xeitueing eno ti nak myayaing wou xam lek bouk wei Pasova yo. Xam ambei a bong king wei Yudayeiw o nak?” 
\p  
\v 40 Xel taxe elox bei, “Ma, se e! Qe wong Barabas lam wou xa!” Barabas on mi wo vevek me mi panax. 
\c 19  
\s1 Xel wong Yesu la bei xel a tuw e lek xax pepeeng 
\p  
\v 1 Woyom Pailat qou Yesu me la bei xel sesa e.  
\v 2 Xel vevek viy yis qapangek lekti me buwexe nambei qelumking me toung lek e lu. De xel byex teimb ding wei mateyek o ti lek e  
\v 3 de xel lam wou e lumama me neil embei, “Bendiyeing king wei Yudayeiw o!” Dom xel petapexe e ling. 
\p  
\v 4 Pailat loumelam myayaing no me neil wou xel Yudayeiw wei di qekuma yo bei, “Wei, a qou e me na loum myayaing bei xam ghe boulek bei a se xeiwou qayeeng qes ti lek e bei a bo qayeeng en e.”  
\v 5 Om Yesu lam myayaing is qelumking wei qapangek ying wei xel toung lek e lu me teimb ding wei mateyek o de Pailat neil wou xel bei, “Tambiy tiyo inye!” 
\p  
\v 6 Ka xel lumuki leitata me xel xe beyeiv yei moxo, eno xel taxe la bei, “Tuw e lek xax pepeeng! Tuw e lek xax pepeeng!” 
\p Ekom Pailat neil elox wou xel bei, “Xam venaxow qou e me tuw lek xax pepeeng, en ay eno a se xeiwou qayeeng qes ti bei a bo qayeeng en e.” 
\p  
\v 7 Lei ngandoung wei Yudayeiw neil elox bei, “Xe xe petieing ti, me petieing tiyon neil embei e mey, en emaxow neil embei e Anutu Neu Moux.” 
\p  
\v 8 Pailat ngo tine, eno moxo yaleeng ngandoung mouyo,  
\v 9 de moxo lox lalei eivek xomek seyap. Me teling wou Yesu, “Wang lam anghei inya?” Ekom Yesu se neil lulti wou e.  
\v 10 Pailat neil, “Wambei se baluk wou ay? Wa seng woulek bei a xe nikanzek teyei bei bo wang na myayaing o na tuw wang lek xax pepeeng?” 
\p  
\v 11 Yesu neil elox bei, “Wa se xe nikanzek ti ghanaw ay, wangwei Anutu se bong wou wang anghei gheyapu nei. Nambei nyon om tambiy tiwei qou a me lam wou wang ne eno wo sewokeing ghanaw wang veil.” 
\p  
\v 12 Woyom Pailat di wong me yei en embei bo Yesu na myayaing, ekom xel lei ngandoung wei Yudayeiw eno taxe la bei, “Wangwei wang bong tambiy tine na ond wa se gweleeng wei Sisa yo. Tambiy ti embei neimbei emaxow king ond wo vevek wou Sisa.” 
\p  
\v 13 Pailat ngo tine, eno moxo qou Yesu me la myayaing me deilek sia wei tambiy wei mi ngo qayeeng o nanghei beyeeng wei xel mi neil qakous zek o. Eivek Hibru vyend eno xel mi neil Gabata.  
\v 14 Inye bouk wei Menyexeing lulul lek Sounda tiwei Pasova yo, inyon nambei seivma evlek. 
\p Pailat neil wou xel Yudayeiw, “Inye xam xe king.” 
\p  
\v 15 Ekom xel taxe la bei, “Qou e me la veil! Qou e me la veil! De tuw e lek xax pepeeng!” 
\p Pailat teling, “Teyei bei a tuw xam xe king lek xax pepeeng?” 
\p Xel lumuki leitata lewexe bei, “Xa se xe king ti qe Sisa venaxow.” 
\p  
\v 16 Om Pailat wong e la wou xel bei xel atuw e lek xax pepeeng. 
\s1 Xel tuw Yesu lek xax pepeeng 
\p Om xel vevek qou Yesu me la.  
\v 17 De emaxow qalei e xe xax pepeeng me xel la beyeeng tiwei xel mi taxe lukanzek o. Eivek Hibru vyend eno xel mi taxe bei Golgata.  
\v 18 Nanghei inyon eno xel tuw e lek xax pepeeng is luw yayuw, nge wou valu de nge wou valu de Yesu eivek senghoing. 
\p  
\v 19 Pailat byex qayeeng ti me tuw lek xax pepeeng, qayeeng tine neil ambei nye: YESU WEI NASARET O, KING WEI YUDAYEIW O.  
\v 20 Yudayeiw ngenong pyaw dee tiyon, en beyeeng wei xel tuw Yesu lek xax pepeeng on toundei paviy beyeeng ngandoung, dee tiyon xel byex eivek Hibru vyend, me Rom me Grik.  
\v 21 De xel lumuki leitata wei Yudayeiw eno neil elox wou Pailat, “Wa se byex bei ‘King wei Yudayeiw o ti,’ qe tambiy tine neil embei, ‘A king wei Yudayeiw o.’” 
\p  
\v 22 Pailat lewexe bei, “Vati wei a byex, eno e toumendei nambei a byex woy.” 
\p  
\v 23 Xel vevek tuw Yesu lek xax pepeeng woy, eno xel qou e xe teimb dalus me dembu e la qendu vey, ti wou xel titi, is teimb ding wei xel duw en qaeing tixemou nanghei kwa me e la vaxa yo. 
\p  
\v 24 Xel neil wouma bei, “Xey ambei se zex teimb tine qe xey ambei banex qakous dee me na ghei bei eti tyek na qou.” 
\p Tiyon la teyei lek xoulek wei di yeip eivek qapiya wei neil embei, 
\q1 “Xel dembu a xe teimb wouma eivek xel venaxow senghoing 
\q2 de xel nex qakous dee en a xe teimb ding.” \rq Qapiya Lalo 22:18\rq* 
\m Om inye vati wei xel vevek wong o. 
\p  
\v 25 Paviy Yesu xe xax pepeeng eno ta me ta li vex toukale, me Maria wei Klopas venei me Maria wei Makdala yo.  
\v 26 Gyeik ingwei Yesu yei ta nanghei inyon me betiyeing tiwei e lalei vind o toukale paviyeing, eno Moxo neil wou ta, “Vex wei, wa neum moux inyon,”  
\v 27 woyom neil wou betiyeing tiyon bei, “Wei, vex tiyon wa tam.” Lek bouk kayon me e mi la, eno betiyeing tiyon qou vexo me la e maxow beeng. 
\s1 Yesu xe meyeing 
\p  
\v 28 Kalekom Yesu woulek bei lulul dalus la wou eivek en kandek xoulek wei di yeip eivek qapiya eno bo neing lek, de Yesu neil embei, “A kwang tip.”  
\v 29 Deng wain senyeing ti toundei inyei, om xel toung balam eivek wain me e pup, dom tup lek xax hisop mema de zeim e lek la wou Yesu mya.  
\v 30 Yesu num wain ma, eno neil embei, “Moxo ma yo.” De ivma eivek dom wong nulaweeng la. 
\p  
\v 31 Bouk tiyon inye bouk wei Menyexeing wou lulul o, de yanyeing eno inye bouk ngandoung wei Sabat o. Om xel lei ngandoung wei Yudayeiw embei xel neing se toungami lek xax pepeeng lek bouk wei Sabat o, om xel teling wou Pailat bei xel na pyaw xel vaxend apek de zewax xel neing veil.  
\v 32 Om xel vevek la pyaw tambiy nge myaxeeng wei tumilek xax pepeeng wou Yesu byek o vaxa pek. De woyom xel la pyaw nge wei tumi wou e byek valu yo.  
\v 33 Ekom gyeik ingwei xel lam wou Yesu eno xel yei bei mey woy, om xel se pyaw e vaxa luw xouing.  
\v 34 Ekom xel vevek ti beum Yesu byek en yiy, de lutika eno gyand aluw memiing lam.  
\v 35 De tambiy tiwei yeimalek eno neil qayeeng en, me e xe qayeeng on wo neing. Moxo woulek bei neil zonghek. Om neilteyei en kandek xam ghe bongis ambei nyon.  
\v 36 Lulul ti beimambei yon la teyei lek en kandek xoulek wei di yeip eivek qapiya yo bo neing lek: 
\q1 “Tyek xel se pyaw e kanzek ti pek.” \rq Qouloum 12:46; Pyamema wou 9:12; Qapiya Lalo 34:20\rq* 
\m  
\v 37 De qayeeng nge neil ambei nye, 
\q1 “Tyek xel mendi gyei tambiy tiwei xel beum o.” \rq Sakarias 12:10\rq* 
\s1 Xel ev Yesu 
\p  
\v 38 Kalekom Yosep wei Arimatia yo la teling wou Pailat en Yesu neing. Yosep on Yesu xe betiyeing ti, ekom mindei xupekeing en nambei yaleeng en xel lei ngandoung wei Yudayeiw. Pailat lewexe lek e om la qou Yesu neing me la.  
\v 39 Nikodimas, tambiy tiwei takwei eno la wou Yesu eivek boukeing eno la is Yosep me qou wel xeimangou wei xel maleeng xax mer me aloes myalouk lekti yo me lam. Nimaying teyei lek xoumeeng yal (30) kilo.  
\v 40 Tambiy yuw on qou Yesu neing me pelei wel wei xeimangou yo lek de beliv eivek qaeing teleing teyei lek Yudayeiw xe kwa wei xel mi ev xel meyeing o.  
\v 41 Eivek beyeeng wei xel tuw Yesu lek xax pepeeng nanghei yon eno xuk ti toundei inyon, de eivek xuk tiyon eno leiveeng meyeing vako ti toundei, xel seng ghei liw xelti eivek.  
\v 42 En inyon nambei Yudayeiw xe bouk wei menyexeing lulul o de nambei leiveeng meyeing tiyon toundei paviy, om luw lak liw Yesu eivek nanghei inyon. 
\c 20  
\s1 Yesu qandi lek veil meyeing 
\p  
\v 1 Satiboukeing lul wei di nexla lek bouk ti myaxeeng wei sounda tiyon, eno Maria wei Makdala la ingwei leiveeng meyeing nei me yei bei qakous tatekexe veil leiveeng mya.  
\v 2 Om vexo veimya me loum neil wou Simon Petele luw betiyeing nge wei Yesu lalei mi vind o, me neil embei, “Xel qou Tambiy Ngandoung veil leiveeng meyeing, de xa se woulek ingwei xel liw anghei yo.” 
\p  
\v 3 Om Petele luw betiyeing nge yon qandi me la ingwei leiveeng meyeing nei.  
\v 4 Luw xouing veimyend me la, ekom betiyeing nge yon veimya me ghanaw Petele me la ingwei leiveeng meyeing nei tax.  
\v 5 Moxo dundek me yeila qaeing di yeip inyon, ekom se la lalei.  
\v 6 Woyom Simon Petele betiy e me la inyon, me eivek la lalei me yei qaeing wei di yeip inyon o,  
\v 7 ka yei qaeing nge wei xel tup e vivekwou Yesu lu, eno xelti pyaw me toung beyaleing veil qaeing ba.  
\v 8 Woyom betiyeing nge wei la leiveeng meyeing nei tax, eno la lalei is ambei nyon. Moxo yei me wongis.  
\v 9 Neing, xoulek wei yeip eivek qapiya bei Yesu qandi lek veil meyeing eno xel seng ghei woulek.  
\v 10 Woyom betiyeing aluw lox me la bend. 
\s1 Yesu talex xow wou Maria wei Makdala 
\p  
\v 11 Ekom Maria toukale myayaing paviy leiveeng meyeing me di eng. Ka vexo di eng, vexo dundek me yeila leiveeng meyeing lalei.  
\v 12 Me yei angela yayuw is teimb wei teltyip o. Luw toundei wou kawei xel liw Yesu neing lek o, nge toundei wou e lu de nge toundei wou e vaxa. 
\p  
\v 13 Luw teling wou vexo bei, “Vex, wang eng en vati?” Vexo neil embei, “Xel qou a xe Tambiy Ngandoung, de a se woulek bei xel liw e nanghei inya.” 
\p  
\v 14 Maria neil ambei nyon de pekwi ma me yei e vivekwou eno yei Yesu toukale inyon, ekom vexo se yeimawou bei inyon Yesu. 
\p  
\v 15 Yesu neil embei, “Vex, nambei nya wang di eng? Eti ingwei wang di wimexe yon?” 
\p Maria embeik nge inyon tambiy wei mi yeiteyei xuk o, om vexo neil wou bei, “Teiv wangwei wa qalei e me na nei, ond wa neil wou ay en ingwei wang liw e nanghei yo, en kandek a na qou moxo.” 
\p  
\v 16 Yesu neil wou vexo, “Maria.” 
\p De vexo pekwi ma me neil wou e eivek Hibru vyend, “Rabuni” qes ambei nye Putoung. 
\p  
\v 17 Yesu neil embei, “Wa seng daxlek ay, en a se ghei lox gheyapu wou Mang. Wang nox wou a lingyeiw me na neil wou xel, ambei nox me na wou Mang me xam Mamim, wou a xe Anutu me xam xe Anutu.” 
\p  
\v 18 Maria wei Makdala yo lox wou xel betiyeing me neil embei, “A xei Tambiy Ngandoung!” De vexo neil wou xel en qayeeng wei moxo neil wou e yo. 
\s1 Yesu talex xow wou e xe xel betiyeing 
\p  
\v 19 Lek soukeing wei bouk ti myaxeeng wei sounda tiyon, xel betiyeing qekuma, eno xel toung qapomb beimambei yond zeyi en xel yaleeng en lei ngandoung wei Yudayeiw, eno Yesu lam me nale eivek xel senghoing me neil, “Lalei vevopeing e mi mendei is xam.”  
\v 20 Ka moxo neil ambei nyon woy, moxo talex mema luw me byek wou xel. De xel betiyeing wo xeindlala ngandoung gyeik ingwei xel yei Tambiy Ngandoung o. 
\p  
\v 21 Yesu neil no bei, “Lalei vevopeing e mi mendei is xam! Nambei ingwei Mang wong a lam. De a wong xam ghe la.”  
\v 22 De is inyon eno moxo vei mya laweeng la lek xel de neil embei, “Xam ghe qou Laweeng Vambuing.  
\v 23 Wangwei xam semaleeng sewokeing wei xelti yo, on tyek Anutu semaleeng sewokeing veil. Ek wangwei xam se semaleeng sewokeing wei xelti yo, ond tyek Anutu se semaleeng sewokeing veil.” 
\s1 Yesu talex xow wou Tomas 
\p  
\v 24 Tomas wei xel mi taxe Didimas, xel xoumeeng yuw eno ti, se toundei is xel betiyeing gyeik ingwei Yesu lam o.  
\v 25 Om xel betiyeing ba neil wou e bei, “Xa xei Tambiy Ngandoung!” 
\p Ekom moxo neil wou xel bei, “Wangwei a se ghei beleim mya me na toung memang deyis eivek e mema luw, me na toung memang eivek yiy mya wei e byek o, ond tyek a se bongis.” 
\p  
\v 26 Ka sounda qes ti la veil eno e xe xel betiyeing lox me la dei eivek xomek no, me Tomas toundei is xel. De xel toung qapomb zeyi, Yesu lam nale eivek xel senghoing me neil embei, “Lalei vevopeing e mi mendei is xam.”  
\v 27 Woyom moxo neil wou Tomas bei, “Toung memam deyis lam inye me wei a memang aluw. De tatei memam lam me toung eivek a byek. Tip laleim yuw de wongis.” 
\p  
\v 28 Tomas neil wou e, “A xe Tambiy ngandoung me a xe Anutu.” 
\p  
\v 29 Woyom Yesu neil wou e bei, “En nambei wang wei ay om wang wongis, xeilala e mendei is eti yeiw wei se yei ay qe xel wongis o.” 
\s1 Yoan neil qes wei qapiya ne 
\p  
\v 30 Yesu wong dee wei lulvako eno ngenong eivek e xe xel betiyeing mendghalus, ekom xel se byex eivek qapiya tine.  
\v 31 Ekom qayeeng ti beimambei wei a byex ne eno xam a mi bongis bei Yesu e Kilisi, me Anutu Neu Moux, de nangya wongeingis tiyon eno tyek xam a qou mapieing eivek e lei. 
\c 21  
\s1 Yesu talex xow wou xel betiyeing lim yuw 
\p  
\v 1 Kalekom Yesu talex xow wou e xe xel betiyeing no, nanghei lounyeing wei Taiberias nei. Inyon qandi nambei nye:  
\v 2 Simon Petele, me Tomas wei xel mi taxe e lei nge Didimas, me Natanael wei Kana eivek Galili yo, de Sebedi neu luw, me betiyeing yayuw is eno xel xouing toundei lekti.  
\v 3 Simon Petele neil wou xel bei, “Ambei na qou woing.” De xel neil embei, “Xa bei na is wang.” Om xel la myayaing me la dei eivek bot, ekom boukeing tiyon eno xel se qou lulti. 
\p  
\v 4 Satiboukeing lul eno Yesu toukale wou mamileeng vi, ekom xel betiyeing se woulek bei inyei Yesu. 
\p  
\v 5 Woyom moxo taxe la wou xel bei, “Xam neungyeiw, xam ghe qou woing valu?” 
\p Xel neil elox bei, “Ma.” 
\p  
\v 6 Moxo neil embei, “Xam banex xam xe lewek na eivek bot nenya valu wei payeiv o on tyek xam a qou valu.” Om xel wong ambei nyon, eno xel se teyei bei puw lewek noum en nambei woing on ngenongakes. 
\p  
\v 7 Woyom betiyeing tiwei Yesu lalei mi vind eno neil wou Petele bei, “Inyei Tambiy Ngandoung!” Ka Simon Petele ngo moxo neil embei, “Inyei Tambiy Ngandoung,” om byex e xe teimb ding lek, en kwax veil de di wong xuk. De vyeip me la eivek memiing.  
\v 8 De xel betiyeing bamba di betiwou e eivek bot, de xel puw lewek wei pup en woing eno lam, en xel se toundei dingta veil nenyawes, inye nambei 100 mita.  
\v 9 Ka xel lam nenyawes eno xel yei nenyex bapax ti di tum de woing toundei lek, me belet valu is. 
\p  
\v 10 Yesu neil wou xel, “Xam a qou woing wei xam ghe qou yon valu me ghe nam.” 
\p  
\v 11 Simon Petele lek bot me la dandiy lewek la nenyawes. Inye pup en woing ngandoung teyei lek 153, xel woing ne ngenong ekom lewek se lex.  
\v 12 Yesu neil wou xel, “Xam lam wa.” Xel betiyeing yaleeng om ti se teling e bei, “Inyon wang eti?” En xel woulek bei inye Tambiy Ngandoung.  
\v 13 Yesu lam qou belet me wong wou xel de wong ambei nyon wou woing is.  
\v 14 Tine inye luyal en ingwei Yesu talex xow wou e xe xel betiyeing gyeik ingwei qandi veil meyeing o. 
\s1 Yesu neil wou Petele bei e mi gyeiteyei sipsip 
\p  
\v 15 Ka xel ya woy, eno Yesu neil wou Simon Petele bei, “Simon Yoan neu, beip wa laleim vind ay zonghek ghanaw xel ne?” 
\p Moxo neil embei, “Ee, Tambiy Ngandoung, wang woulek bei a laleing vind wang.” 
\p Yesu neil embei, “Wa mi bet a xe sipsip lingheing ne.” 
\p  
\v 16 Yesu neil no, “Simon Yoan neu, wa laleim vind Ay zonghek?” 
\p Moxo lewexe bei, “Ee, Tambiy Ngandoung, wang woulek bei a laleing vind wang.” 
\p Yesu neil embei, “Wa mi gweiteyei a xe sipsip.” 
\p  
\v 17 Luyal eno moxo neil wou e, “Simon Yoan neu, wa laleim vind ay?” 
\p Petele lalei wo maying en nambei Yesu teling e luyal, “Wa laleim vind ay?” Moxo neil embei, “Tambiy Ngandoung, wang woulek lulul dalus, om wang woulek bei a laleing vind wang.” 
\p Yesu neil embei, “Wa mi bet a xe sipsip.  
\v 18 A neil wou wang zonghek, gyeik ingwei wa ghavis eno wang vunekwou xow me ghe la teyei lek ingwei wang wou naleim en o, ekom gyeik ingwei wang wo teiv eno tyek wa tatei memam luw xouing na, de xel valu tyek bunekwou wang me na qou wang me na ingwei wa bei seng na yo.”  
\v 19 Yesu neil tine en sakwaing wei Petele tyek na mey de bo lei ngandoung wou Anutu yo. Woyom neil wou moxo bei, “Wang nam betiwou ay!” 
\p  
\v 20 Petele pekwi ma me yei betiyeing tiwei Yesu lalei vind eno di betiwou luw. Inyon tambiy tiwei liw lu la lek Yesu bambou me neil, “Tambiy Ngandoung, eti tyek na neil wang teyei me na toung wang na eivek xel ba memend?”  
\v 21 Ka Petele yei e, eno moxo teling bei, “Tambiy ngandoung nambei nya wou e?” 
\p  
\v 22 Yesu neil elox bei, “Wangwei a neimbei e toumendei mapieing deka a noum le, ond inye wo vati wou wang? Wa betiwou ay.”  
\v 23 Om pavulek la wo sapa eivek xel betiyeing, xel di neil embei betiyeing tine tyek se mey. Ekom Yesu se neil embei moxo tyek se mey, qe neil embei, “Wangwei a laleing devind bei e toumendei mapieing ond tyek na toumendei deka a noum le, ond inye wo vati wou wang?” 
\p  
\v 24 Tine inye betiyeing tiwei neil qayeeng neing en lulul ti beimambei ne de byex dalus eivek qapiya. Me xey a woulek bei e xe qayeeng ne zonghek. 
\p  
\v 25 Yesu wong lulul ngenong valu is ambei nyon. Om wangwei xel a byex dalus nei, ond tyek beyeeng wei tembuing ne na ma en ingwei xey ambei toung qapiya eivek o.